381    /**
382     * acceptTrade(TradeReportStruct externalTradeStruct) Gets the BT/EFP information from the param
383     * Calls the createTrade() method which creates and persists the trade, and publishes for CTM
384     * and SIAC?? returns the TradeReportStruct, with the tradeId populated.
385     * 
386     * @param externalTradeStruct Information about the Block Trade, or EFP Trade entered by the
387     * Help Desk
388 * @exception   SystemException -       Thrown by createTrade()
389 * @exception   CommunicationException - May be thrown by isValid()
390 * @exception   AuthorizationException - -same-
391     * @exception DataValidationException - if the product being traded Product not found for given
392     * productKey
393     * @exception NotAcceptedException - if the trade being accepted is a REGULAR_TRADE, or if the
394     * product being traded is a strategy
395     * @exception TransactionFailedException - if the attempt to persist fails for any reason ?? the
396     * method used by Manual stock trade report was overwritten in TradeServiceStockImpl
397     */
398 
399    public TradeReportStruct acceptTrade(TradeReportStruct externalTradeStruct)
400            throws SystemException, CommunicationException, AuthorizationException,
401            DataValidationException, NotAcceptedException, TransactionFailedException
402{
403    TradeReportStructV2 theTrade = doPreProcess(externalTradeStruct);
404    TradeReportStructV2 acceptedTrade = acceptTradeV2(theTrade);
405    return acceptedTrade.tradeReport;
406}
407 
408private TradeReportStructV2 doPreProcess(TradeReportStruct externalTradeStruct)
409{
410        if (Log.isDebugOn())
411        {
412            Log.debug(this, "In " + getClass().getName() + ".acceptTrade");
413    }
414    TradeReportStructV2 theTrade = new TradeReportStructV2();
415        // set the default current trade setllement date as today, and set transaction time with
416        // current time
417        theTrade.settlementTradeReport = com.cboe.domain.util.StructBuilder
418                .buildDefaultTradeReportSettlement();
419    theTrade.tradeReport = externalTradeStruct;
420    return theTrade;
421}
422 
423    public TradeReportStruct acceptTradeWithClearingType(TradeReportStruct externalTrade,
424            boolean isParTrade, char tradedSide, AtomicCmtaAllocationStruct[] atomicCmtaAllocations)
425            throws SystemException, CommunicationException, AuthorizationException,
426            DataValidationException, NotAcceptedException, TransactionFailedException
427    {
428        testARException(externalTrade, tradedSide);
429        TradeReportStructV2 theTrade = doPreProcess(externalTrade);
430        short handlingInstructions = TradeReportHandlingInstructions.REGULAR;
431        
432        TradeReportStructV2 acceptedTrade = acceptTradeV2(theTrade, handlingInstructions,
433                isParTrade, tradedSide, atomicCmtaAllocations);
434 
435        if (isParTrade)
436        { /* The par trade has to be TradeSources.PAR */
437            // this is for manual trade only.
438            acceptedTrade.tradeReport.tradeSource = TradeSources.PAR;
439        }
440        
441        return acceptedTrade.tradeReport;
442    }
443    
444    public TradeReportStruct acceptTradeWithClearingType(TradeReportStruct externalTrade,
445            boolean isParTrade, char tradedSide,
446            AtomicCmtaAllocationStruct[] atomicCmtaAllocations, char[] clearingTypes,
447            boolean sweepTrade) throws SystemException, CommunicationException,
448            AuthorizationException, DataValidationException, NotAcceptedException,
449            TransactionFailedException
450    {
451        testARException(externalTrade, tradedSide);
452        TradeReportStructV2 theTrade = doPreProcess(externalTrade);
453        short handlingInstructions = TradeReportHandlingInstructions.REGULAR;
454 
455        TradeReportStructV2 acceptedTrade = acceptTradeV2(theTrade, handlingInstructions,
456                isParTrade, tradedSide, atomicCmtaAllocations, clearingTypes, sweepTrade);
457 
458        if (isParTrade)
459        { /* The par trade has to be TradeSources.PAR */
460            // this is for manual trade only.
461            acceptedTrade.tradeReport.tradeSource = TradeSources.PAR;
462        }
463 
464        return acceptedTrade.tradeReport;
465    }
466    
467    private TradeReport acceptManualTradeWithClearingType(TradeReportStruct externalTrade,
468            boolean isParTrade, char tradedSide, AtomicCmtaAllocationStruct[] atomicCmtaAllocations, char [] clearingTypes, boolean sweepTrade, boolean turnOffPersistent)
469            throws SystemException, CommunicationException, AuthorizationException,
470            DataValidationException, NotAcceptedException, TransactionFailedException
471    {
472        testARException(externalTrade, tradedSide);
473        TradeReportStructV2 theTrade = doPreProcess(externalTrade);
474        short handlingInstructions = TradeReportHandlingInstructions.REGULAR;
475 
476        TradeReport acceptedTrade = acceptManualTradeV2(theTrade, handlingInstructions,
477                isParTrade, tradedSide, atomicCmtaAllocations, clearingTypes, sweepTrade, turnOffPersistent);
478 
479        if (isParTrade)
480        { /* The par trade has to be TradeSources.PAR */
481            // this is for manual trade only.
482            ((TradeReportImpl)acceptedTrade).setTradeSource(TradeSources.PAR);
483        }
484 
485        return acceptedTrade;
486    }
487    
488    private boolean isParentProduct(int productKey)
489    {
490        boolean isParentProduct = false;
491        ProductData prodData;
492        try
493        {
494            prodData = getProductDataCacheHome().find().getProductData(productKey);
495            isParentProduct = prodData.isStrategy();
496        }
497        catch (Exception e)
498        {
499            // This shouldn't really happen. So for now, let's just swallow the 
500            // exception and move on.
501            Log.information("Encountered exception while attempting to confirm whetherOther product is strategy-product/");
502        }        
503        return isParentProduct;
504    }
505    
506    public TradeReportStruct[] acceptManualTrade(ManualTradeReportStruct p_externalTrade,
507            boolean sweepTrade) throws SystemException, CommunicationException,
508            AuthorizationException, DataValidationException, NotAcceptedException,
509            TransactionFailedException
510    {
511        ClearingTradeReportStruct [] trades = p_externalTrade.tradeReports;
512        List<TradeReport> tradeReports = new ArrayList<TradeReport>(trades.length);
513        TradeReport parentTradeReport = null;
514        boolean isStrategyTraded = false;
515        for (int i = 0; i < trades.length; i++)
516        {
517            TradeReport theReport = acceptManualTradeWithClearingType(trades[i].tradeReport, trades[i].isParTrade, trades[i].tradedSide, trades[i].atomicCmtaAllocations, 
518                    trades[i].manualReportTypes, sweepTrade, true);
519            tradeReports.add(theReport);
520            if (isParentProduct(trades[i].tradeReport.productKey)) {
521                parentTradeReport = theReport;
522                isStrategyTraded = true;
523            }
524        }
525        if (isStrategyTraded && parentTradeReport != null)
526        {
527            assignParentReport(tradeReports, parentTradeReport);
528        }
529        TradeReportStruct[] theReturnedStruct = new TradeReportStruct[tradeReports.size()];
530        int j = 0;
531        for (TradeReport theReport : tradeReports) {
532            theReturnedStruct[j++] = theReport.toStruct(true);
533        }
534        return theReturnedStruct;
535    }
536 
537    private void assignParentReport(List<TradeReport> acceptedTrades, TradeReport parentTradeReport)
538    {
539        if (parentTradeReport == null) {
540            Log.debug(this, "Unable to assign the Parent trade report - " + parentTradeReport.getTradeId());
541        }
542        Transaction.startTransaction();
543        for (TradeReport theReport : acceptedTrades) {
544            long theTradeId = theReport.getTradeId();
545            if (theTradeId != parentTradeReport.getTradeId()) {
546               ((TradeReportImpl)theReport).setParentReport(parentTradeReport);
547            }
548        }
549        Transaction.commit();
550    }
551    /**
552     * Create a trade for the linkage order filled for underlying order as result of Auto Link to
553     * away exchange.
554     */
555    public long createTradeForLinkageFill(OrderStruct underlyingOrder,
556            FilledReportStruct fillReport, OrderStruct linkageOrderStruct,
557            DateTimeStruct transactionTime, String p_executingBroker)
558                                            throws  DataValidationException, SystemException
559    {
560            long tradeDbId = 0;
561            
562        if(Log.isDebugOn())
563        {
564            Log.debug(this, "In " + getClass().getName()+ ".createTradeForLinkageFill");
565        }
566        boolean sweepNReturnTrade = false;
567        if(p_executingBroker != null && p_executingBroker.trim().length() > 0)
568            sweepNReturnTrade = true;
569        TradeReportStruct tradeReportStruct = getTradeReport(fillReport, underlyingOrder,
570                linkageOrderStruct, transactionTime, p_executingBroker);
571        AtomicCmtaAllocationStruct[] atomicCmtaAllocations = getAtomicCmtaAllocations(
572                tradeReportStruct, underlyingOrder, linkageOrderStruct, fillReport);
573 
574        String outboundVendor = getOutbounVendorsForAutoLinkTrades(linkageOrderStruct);
575        
576        TradeReportStructV2 theTrade = doPreProcess(tradeReportStruct);
577        Price price = PriceFactory.create(theTrade.tradeReport.price);
578        TradingProduct product;
579        try
580        {
581            product = getTradingProductHome().findByKey(theTrade.tradeReport.productKey);
582        }
583        catch (NotFoundException e)
584        {
585            // this was already validated in isValidTrade
586            String message = "Unable to access trading prodcut for product key "
587                    + theTrade.tradeReport.productKey;
588            Log.exception(this, message, e);
589            throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException(message,
590                    DataValidationCodes.INVALID_PRODUCT);
591        }
592 
593        if (Log.isDebugOn())
594        {
595            Log.debug(this, "TradeServiceImpl.createTrade creating a manual trade...");
596        }
597 
598        TradeReportImpl tradeReport = (TradeReportImpl) getTradeReportHome().create(product,
599                theTrade.tradeReport.quantity, price, theTrade, getMyIdService(),
600                                                              atomicCmtaAllocations, outboundVendor, sweepNReturnTrade);
601 
602        tradeDbId = tradeReport.getObjectIdentifierAsLong();
603        
604        logAfterTradeReportCreation(product, theTrade.tradeReport.quantity, price,
605                TradeReportHandlingInstructions.REGULAR, theTrade, tradeReport);
606        
607        return tradeDbId;
608    }
609        
610        // NOL use for generating Trade Report
611    private TradeReportStruct getTradeReport(FilledReportStruct fillReport,
612            OrderStruct underlyingOrderStruct, OrderStruct linkageOrderStruct,
613            DateTimeStruct transactionTime, String executingBroker)
614    {
615        TradeReportStruct tradeReport = TradeReportStructBuilder.buildTradeReportStruct();
616        // populate tradereport from fillreportstruct.
617        
618        tradeReport.tradeSource = TradeSources.SYSTEM;
619        tradeReport.tradeType = TradeTypes.NO_PRINT_LINKAGE_TRADE;
620        tradeReport.sessionName = underlyingOrderStruct.activeSession;
621        tradeReport.productKey = underlyingOrderStruct.productKey;
622        tradeReport.quantity = fillReport.tradedQuantity;
623        tradeReport.price = fillReport.price;
624        tradeReport.businessDate = new DateWrapper(TradingSessionNameHelper
625                .getSession(fillReport.sessionName).businessDay).toDateStruct();
626        long transTimeInMillis = DateWrapper.convertToMillis(transactionTime);
627        tradeReport.timeTraded.date = DateWrapper.convertToDate(transTimeInMillis);
628        tradeReport.timeTraded.time = DateWrapper.convertToTime(transTimeInMillis);
629 
630        ArrayList<AtomicTradeStruct> atomicTradeStructList = new ArrayList<AtomicTradeStruct>();
631        atomicTradeStructList = populateAtomicTrade(fillReport, underlyingOrderStruct,
632                linkageOrderStruct, executingBroker);
633 
634        if(atomicTradeStructList.size() > 0)
635        {
636            tradeReport.parties = new AtomicTradeStruct[atomicTradeStructList.size()];
637            tradeReport.parties = atomicTradeStructList
638                    .toArray(new AtomicTradeStruct[atomicTradeStructList.size()]);
639        }
640 
641        return tradeReport;
642    }
643    
644    private String getOutbounVendorsForAutoLinkTrades(OrderStruct linkageOrderStruct)
645    {
646        String extensions = linkageOrderStruct.extensions;
647        String outboundVendor = "";
648 
649        if (extensions !=null) 
650        {
651            try 
652            {
653                ExtensionsHelper extensionHelper = new ExtensionsHelper(extensions);
654                outboundVendor = extensionHelper.getValue(ExtensionFields.BROKER_ROUTING_ID);
655            } 
656            catch(ParseException pe) 
657            {
658                Log.alarm("Cannot parse the Extensions - Outbound Vendor field for linkage order "
659                        + pe.getMessage());
660            }
661            
662        }
663        return outboundVendor;
664    }
665    
666    /**
667     * These are the new fields passed to Trade Report for the CMTA Allocation for manual trades per
668     * contra.
669     * 
670     * @param tradeReports
671     * @return
672     */
673    private AtomicCmtaAllocationStruct[] getAtomicCmtaAllocations(TradeReportStruct tradeReport,
674            OrderStruct anOrderStruct, OrderStruct linkageOrderStruct, FilledReportStruct fillReport)
675    {
676     
677        String awayExchange = "";
678        try
679        {
680            ExtensionsHelper extensionsHelper =  new ExtensionsHelper(fillReport.extensions);
681            awayExchange = extensionsHelper.getValue(ExtensionFields.EXCHANGE_DESTINATION);
682        }
683        catch(ParseException pe)
684        {
685        }
686 
687        AtomicCmtaAllocationStruct[] atomicCmtaAllocations = null;
688        AtomicTradeStruct[] atomicTrades = tradeReport.parties;
689        atomicCmtaAllocations = new AtomicCmtaAllocationStruct[atomicTrades.length];
690        
691        for(int i = 0; i < atomicTrades.length; i++)
692        {
693            AtomicCmtaAllocationStruct atomicCmtaAllocationStruct = AtomicCmtaAllocationStructBuilder
694                    .buildAtomicCmtaAllocationStructBuilder();
695            
696            atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.atomicTradeId = atomicTrades[i].atomicTradeId;
697            if(anOrderStruct.side == Sides.BUY)
698            {
699                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.buyerAwayExchangeAcronym = new ExchangeAcronymStruct(
700                        awayExchange, "");
701                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.buyerOrderDate = anOrderStruct.orderId.orderDate;
702                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.buyerOrsid = anOrderStruct.orsId;
703                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.buyerSupressionReason = 0;
704                
705                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.sellerAwayExchangeAcronym = new ExchangeAcronymStruct(
706                        "", "");
707                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.sellerOrderDate = linkageOrderStruct.orderId.orderDate;
708                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.sellerOrsid = linkageOrderStruct.orsId;
709                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.sellerSupressionReason = 0;
710 
711            }
712            else
713            {
714                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.sellerAwayExchangeAcronym = new ExchangeAcronymStruct(
715                        awayExchange, "");
716                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.sellerOrderDate = anOrderStruct.orderId.orderDate;
717                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.sellerOrsid = anOrderStruct.orsId;
718                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.sellerSupressionReason = 0;
719                
720                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.buyerAwayExchangeAcronym = new ExchangeAcronymStruct("",
721                        "");
722                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.buyerOrderDate = linkageOrderStruct.orderId.orderDate;
723                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.buyerOrsid = linkageOrderStruct.orsId;
724                atomicCmtaAllocationStruct.buyerSupressionReason = 0;
725 
726            }
727            atomicCmtaAllocations[i] = atomicCmtaAllocationStruct;
728        }
729        return atomicCmtaAllocations;
730    }
731 
732    private ArrayList<AtomicTradeStruct> populateAtomicTrade(FilledReportStruct fillReport,
733            OrderStruct underlyingOrderStruct, OrderStruct linkageOrderStruct,
734            String executingBroker)
735    {
736        ArrayList<AtomicTradeStruct> atomicTradeStructList = new ArrayList<AtomicTradeStruct>();
737//        ContraPartyStruct[] contraBrokers = fillReport.contraParties;
738        
739        ContraPartyStruct[] contraBrokers = new ContraPartyStruct[1];
740        ContraPartyStruct contra = new ContraPartyStruct();
741        contra.firm = new ExchangeFirmStruct();
742        contra.firm.exchange = fillReport.executingOrGiveUpFirm.exchange;
743        contra.firm.firmNumber = fillReport.executingOrGiveUpFirm.firmNumber;
744        contra.user = new ExchangeAcronymStruct();
745        contra.user.acronym = defaultLinkageContraUser.acronym;
746        contra.user.exchange = this.anonymousBrokerExchange;
747        contra.quantity = fillReport.tradedQuantity;
748        contraBrokers[0] = contra;
749        
750        String fillReportAccount = (fillReport.account.length() > 16
751                ? fillReport.account.substring(0, 15)
752                : fillReport.account);
753        String fillReportSubAccount = (fillReport.subaccount.length() > 10
754                ? fillReport.subaccount.substring(0, 9)
755                : fillReport.subaccount);
756        fillReport.account = fillReportAccount;
757        fillReport.subaccount = fillReportSubAccount;
758        
759        for(int i = 0; i < contraBrokers.length; i++)
760        {
761            int quantity = contraBrokers[i].quantity;
762            
763            if(quantity <= 0)
764            {
765                continue;
766            }
767            
768            //This checks to see if the contra for the same product exists then add the quantity
769            AtomicTradeStruct atomicTradeForcontra = checkIfContraExistsInList(contraBrokers[i],
770                                          atomicTradeStructList, underlyingOrderStruct.side);
771            
772            if(atomicTradeForcontra != null)
773            {
774                atomicTradeForcontra.quantity = atomicTradeForcontra.quantity + quantity;
775                continue;
776            }
777            
778            AtomicTradeStruct atomicTrade = TradeReportStructBuilder.buildAtomicTradeStruct();
779            atomicTrade.active = true;
780            atomicTrade.sessionName = fillReport.sessionName;
781            long time = System.currentTimeMillis();
782            atomicTrade.entryTime.date = DateWrapper.convertToDate(time);
783            atomicTrade.entryTime.time = DateWrapper.convertToTime(time);
784            atomicTrade.entryType = TradeReportEntryTypes.ADD;
785            atomicTrade.lastEntryType = TradeReportEntryTypes.ADD;
786            atomicTrade.quantity = quantity;
787            
788            if( underlyingOrderStruct.side == Sides.BUY)
789            {
790                //Underlying Order Side
791                atomicTrade.buyerAccount = underlyingOrderStruct.account;
792                if(executingBroker != null && executingBroker.trim().length() > 0)
793                {
794                    atomicTrade.buyerBroker.acronym = executingBroker;
795                }
796                else
797                {
798                    atomicTrade.buyerBroker.acronym = defaultLinkageUser.acronym;
799                }
800                atomicTrade.buyerBroker.exchange = underlyingOrderStruct.userAcronym.exchange;
801                atomicTrade.buyerCmta = underlyingOrderStruct.cmta;
802                atomicTrade.buyerCorrespondentId = underlyingOrderStruct.orderId.correspondentFirm;
803                atomicTrade.buyerFirm = underlyingOrderStruct.orderId.executingOrGiveUpFirm;
804                atomicTrade.buyerFirmBranch = underlyingOrderStruct.orderId.branch;
805                atomicTrade.buyerFirmBranchSequenceNumber = underlyingOrderStruct.orderId.branchSequenceNumber;
806                atomicTrade.buyerOptionalData = underlyingOrderStruct.optionalData;
807 
808                atomicTrade.buyerOrderOrQuote = true;
809 
810                atomicTrade.buyerOrderOrQuoteKey = new CboeIdStruct(
811                        underlyingOrderStruct.orderId.highCboeId,
812                        underlyingOrderStruct.orderId.lowCboeId);
813                atomicTrade.buyerOriginator = underlyingOrderStruct.originator;
814                atomicTrade.buyerPositionEffect = underlyingOrderStruct.positionEffect;
815                atomicTrade.buyerOriginType = underlyingOrderStruct.orderOriginType;
816                atomicTrade.buyerSubaccount = underlyingOrderStruct.subaccount;
817                
818                //Linkage fill Report Side
819                atomicTrade.sellerAccount = fillReport.account;
820                atomicTrade.sellerBroker.acronym = contraBrokers[i].user.acronym;
821                atomicTrade.sellerBroker.exchange = contraBrokers[i].user.exchange;
822                atomicTrade.sellerCmta = fillReport.cmta;
823                atomicTrade.sellerCorrespondentId = linkageOrderStruct.orderId.correspondentFirm;
824                atomicTrade.sellerFirm.firmNumber = contraBrokers[i].firm.firmNumber;
825                atomicTrade.sellerFirm.exchange = contraBrokers[i].firm.exchange;
826                atomicTrade.sellerFirmBranch = linkageOrderStruct.orderId.branch;
827                atomicTrade.sellerFirmBranchSequenceNumber = linkageOrderStruct.orderId.branchSequenceNumber;
828                atomicTrade.sellerOptionalData = fillReport.optionalData;
829 
830                atomicTrade.sellerOrderOrQuote = true;
831 
832                atomicTrade.sellerOrderOrQuoteKey = new CboeIdStruct(
833                        linkageOrderStruct.orderId.highCboeId, linkageOrderStruct.orderId.lowCboeId);
834                atomicTrade.sellerOriginator = fillReport.originator;
835                atomicTrade.sellerPositionEffect = linkageOrderStruct.positionEffect;
836                atomicTrade.sellerOriginType = linkageOrderStruct.orderOriginType;
837                atomicTrade.sellerSubaccount = fillReport.subaccount;
838            }
839            else
840            {
841                //Underlying Order
842                atomicTrade.sellerAccount = underlyingOrderStruct.account;
843                if(executingBroker != null && executingBroker.trim().length() > 0)
844                {
845                    atomicTrade.sellerBroker.acronym = executingBroker;
846                }
847                else
848                {
849                    atomicTrade.sellerBroker.acronym = defaultLinkageUser.acronym;
850                }
851                atomicTrade.sellerBroker.exchange = underlyingOrderStruct.userAcronym.exchange;
852                atomicTrade.sellerCmta = underlyingOrderStruct.cmta;
853                atomicTrade.sellerCorrespondentId = underlyingOrderStruct.orderId.correspondentFirm;
854                atomicTrade.sellerFirm = underlyingOrderStruct.orderId.executingOrGiveUpFirm;
855                atomicTrade.sellerFirmBranch = underlyingOrderStruct.orderId.branch;
856                atomicTrade.sellerFirmBranchSequenceNumber = underlyingOrderStruct.orderId.branchSequenceNumber;
857                atomicTrade.sellerOptionalData = underlyingOrderStruct.optionalData;
858              
859                   atomicTrade.sellerOrderOrQuote = true;
860              
861                atomicTrade.sellerOrderOrQuoteKey = new CboeIdStruct(
862                        underlyingOrderStruct.orderId.highCboeId,
863                        underlyingOrderStruct.orderId.lowCboeId);
864                atomicTrade.sellerOriginator = underlyingOrderStruct.originator;
865                atomicTrade.sellerPositionEffect = underlyingOrderStruct.positionEffect;
866                atomicTrade.sellerOriginType = underlyingOrderStruct.orderOriginType;
867                atomicTrade.sellerSubaccount = underlyingOrderStruct.subaccount;
868                
869                //Linkage side 
870                atomicTrade.buyerAccount = fillReport.account;
871                atomicTrade.buyerBroker.exchange = contraBrokers[i].user.exchange;
872                atomicTrade.buyerBroker.acronym = contraBrokers[i].user.acronym;
873                atomicTrade.buyerCmta = fillReport.cmta;
874                atomicTrade.buyerCorrespondentId = linkageOrderStruct.orderId.correspondentFirm;
875                atomicTrade.buyerFirm.exchange = contraBrokers[i].firm.exchange;
876                atomicTrade.buyerFirm.firmNumber = contraBrokers[i].firm.firmNumber;
877                atomicTrade.buyerFirmBranch = linkageOrderStruct.orderId.branch;
878                atomicTrade.buyerFirmBranchSequenceNumber = linkageOrderStruct.orderId.branchSequenceNumber;
879                atomicTrade.buyerOptionalData = fillReport.optionalData;
880               
881                  atomicTrade.buyerOrderOrQuote = true;
882             
883                atomicTrade.buyerOrderOrQuoteKey = new CboeIdStruct(
884                        linkageOrderStruct.orderId.highCboeId, linkageOrderStruct.orderId.lowCboeId);
885                atomicTrade.buyerOriginator = fillReport.originator;
886                atomicTrade.buyerPositionEffect = linkageOrderStruct.positionEffect;
887                atomicTrade.buyerOriginType = linkageOrderStruct.orderOriginType;
888                atomicTrade.buyerSubaccount = fillReport.subaccount;
889            }
890            
891            atomicTradeStructList.add(atomicTrade);
892        }
893     
894        return atomicTradeStructList;
895    }

897    /**
898     * This return the Atomic trade for the contra if it exists in the list.
899     * 
900     * @param contraBroker
901     * @param atomicTradeStructList
902     * @param side
903     * @return
904     */
905    private AtomicTradeStruct checkIfContraExistsInList(ContraPartyStruct contraBroker,
906            ArrayList<AtomicTradeStruct> atomicTradeStructList, char side)
907    {
908        AtomicTradeStruct atomicTradeForContra = null;
909 
910        for(int contraIndex = 0; contraIndex < atomicTradeStructList.size(); contraIndex++)
911        {
912            AtomicTradeStruct atomicTrade = atomicTradeStructList.get(contraIndex);
913            if(side == Sides.BUY)
914            {
915                if ((atomicTrade.sellerBroker.acronym.equals(contraBroker.user.acronym))
916                        && (atomicTrade.sellerFirm.firmNumber.equals(contraBroker.firm.firmNumber)))
917                {
918                    atomicTradeForContra = atomicTrade;
919                }
920            }
921            else
922            {
923                if ((atomicTrade.buyerBroker.acronym.equals(contraBroker.user.acronym))
924                        && (atomicTrade.buyerFirm.firmNumber.equals(contraBroker.firm.firmNumber)))
925                   {
926                       atomicTradeForContra = atomicTrade;
927                   }
928            }
929        }
930 
931        return atomicTradeForContra;
932 
933    }

960    public TradeReportStructV2 acceptTradeV2(TradeReportStructV2 trade, short handlingInstruction)
961            throws SystemException, CommunicationException, AuthorizationException,
962            DataValidationException, NotAcceptedException, TransactionFailedException
963    {
964    //  overrides passed in PC time on manual trades from SA Gui
965        for (int i = 0; i < trade.tradeReport.parties.length; i++)
966        {
967           trade.tradeReport.parties[i].entryTime.time = TimeServiceWrapper.toDateTimeStruct().time;
968        }
969        TradingProduct product = performPreTradeCreateValidation(trade, handlingInstruction, false);
970        TradeReport tradeReport = null;
971        Price price = null;
972        try
973        {
974            price = PriceFactory.create(trade.tradeReport.price);
975            if (price.isCabinetPrice())
976            {
977                                    Log.information("Cabinet Price Converted to Penny Price for the Fill Report: ");
978                // A constant for the penny would be better.
979                                    price = PriceFactory.create(0.01);
980            }
981            tradeReport = createTrade(product, trade.tradeReport.quantity, price, null,
982                    handlingInstruction, trade, null);
983        }
984        catch (SystemException e)
985        {
986            Log.exception(this, "Exception creating manual Trade Report. " + e.details.message, e);
987            throw e;
988        }
989        try
990        {
991            // execute within product lock, else delegate to class lock:
992            product.acceptCommand(new AcceptTradeCommand(trade.tradeReport.productKey, price
993                    .toStruct()), false);
994        }
995        catch (NotAcceptedException e2)
996        {
997            Log.exception(this, "AcceptTradeCommand not acccpeted for manual TradeReport : "
998                    + e2.toString(), e2);
999            throw e2;
1000        }
1001 
1002        product.setLastTradeTradeId(tradeReport.getTradeId());
1003        return tradeReport.toStructV2(true); // true - include only Active trades
1004    }

1101    private void performPreTradeCreateValidation(TradingProduct product, TradeReportStructV2 trade,
1102            short handlingInstruction) throws NotAcceptedException, DataValidationException,
1103            AuthorizationException, CommunicationException, SystemException
1104    {
1105        if (Log.isDebugOn())
1106        {
1107            Log.debug(this, "In " + getClass().getName() + ".performPreTradeCreateValidation()");
1108        }
1109        
1110        String openSessionName = TradingSessionNameHelper.getOpenConfiguredSessionName();
1111 
1112        if (trade.tradeReport.sessionName == null || openSessionName == null
1113                || !openSessionName.equals(trade.tradeReport.sessionName))
1114        {
1115            String message = "Invalid trading session name: " + trade.tradeReport.sessionName
1116                    + ", current Open Session: " + openSessionName + " at " + getClass().getName()
1117                    + ".performPreTradeCreateValidation().";
1118            Log.alarm(this, message);
1119            throw ExceptionBuilder.notAcceptedException(message, NotAcceptedCodes.INVALID_STATE);
1120        }
1121 
1122        if (product == null)
1123        {
1124            String message = "Invalid product: "+ product + ". Product cannot be null";
1125            Log.alarm(this, message);
1126            throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException(message,
1127                    DataValidationCodes.INVALID_PRODUCT);
1128        }        
1129        
1130        if (handlingInstruction != TradeReportHandlingInstructions.NO_TRADEREPORT_NO_TICKER
1131                && handlingInstruction != TradeReportHandlingInstructions.NO_TICKER
1132                && handlingInstruction != TradeReportHandlingInstructions.REGULAR
1133                && handlingInstruction != TradeReportHandlingInstructions.NO_TRADEREPORT)
1134        {
1135            String message = "Invalid Handling Instruction code passed: " + handlingInstruction
1136                    + " at " + getClass().getName() + ".performPreTradeCreateValidation().";
1137            Log.information(message);
1138            throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException(message,
1139                    DataValidationCodes.INVALID_TRADE_REPORT_HANDLING_INSTRUCTION);
1140        }
1141 
1142        // validate the trade
1143        isValidTrade(trade, product.getProductKeys().productType);
1144    }
1145 
1146    /**
1147     * Creates the billing information for a handheld trade report. It can be extended to support
1148     * other type of trades if needed.
1149     * 
1150     * @param trade: actual trade.
1151     * @param product: product being traded.
1152     * @return array of AtomicTradeBillingStruct containing billing information.
1153     * @throws NotAcceptedException
1154     * 
1155     * @autor Francisco Ojeda
1156     */
1157    private AtomicTradeBillingStruct[] createBillingInfo(TradeReportStructV2 trade,
1158            char tradedSide, TradingProduct product) throws NotAcceptedException
1159    {
1160        if(Log.isDebugOn())
1161    {
1162        Log.debug(this, "In " + getClass().getName() + ".createBillingInfo()");
1163        }
1164 
1165        String DEFAULT_EXCHANGE_ID = " ";
1166        AtomicTradeBillingStruct[] billings = new AtomicTradeBillingStruct[trade.tradeReport.parties.length];
1167 
1168        // add to this check if method is to support other trade types in the future.
1169        if (trade.tradeReport.tradeType == TradeTypes.HANDHELD_TRADE)
1170        {
1171            for (int i = 0; i < billings.length; i++)
1172            {
1173                billings[i] = new AtomicTradeBillingStruct();
1174                billings[i].atomicTradeId = trade.tradeReport.parties[i].atomicTradeId;
1175                billings[i].buyBillingType = BillingTypeIndicators.CROSS;
1176                billings[i].sellBillingType = BillingTypeIndicators.CROSS;
1177                if (tradedSide == Sides.BUY)
1178                {
1179                    billings[i].buyerClearingType = ClearingTypes.CLEAR;
1180                    billings[i].sellerClearingType = ClearingTypes.IGNORE;
1181                }
1182                else if (tradedSide == Sides.SELL)
1183                {
1184                    billings[i].buyerClearingType = ClearingTypes.IGNORE;
1185                    billings[i].sellerClearingType = ClearingTypes.CLEAR;
1186                }
1187                else
1188                {
1189                    String message = "Cannot create billing information for trade side "
1190                            + tradedSide;
1191                    throw ExceptionBuilder.notAcceptedException(message, 0);
1192                }
1193                billings[i].buyAwayExchanges = DEFAULT_EXCHANGE_ID;
1194                billings[i].sellAwayExchanges = DEFAULT_EXCHANGE_ID;
1195            }
1196        }
1197        else
1198        {
1199            String message = "Cannot create billing information for trade type "
1200                    + trade.tradeReport.tradeType;
1201            throw ExceptionBuilder.notAcceptedException(message, 0);
1202        }
1203        return billings;
1204    }

1250    private TradingProduct performPreTradeCreateValidation(TradeReportStructV2 trade,
1251            short handlingInstruction, boolean isParTrade) throws NotAcceptedException,
1252            DataValidationException, AuthorizationException, CommunicationException,
1253            SystemException
1254    {
1255        if (Log.isDebugOn())
1256        {
1257            Log.debug(this, "in " + getClass().getName() + ".acceptTradeV2FromStruct");
1258        }
1259        String openSessionName = TradingSessionNameHelper.getOpenConfiguredSessionName();
1260 
1261        if (!isParTrade)
1262        {
1263            // this is for manual trade only.
1264            trade.tradeReport.tradeSource = TradeSources.MANUAL;
1265        }
1266        if (trade.tradeReport.sessionName == null || openSessionName == null
1267                || !openSessionName.equals(trade.tradeReport.sessionName))
1268        {
1269            String message = "Invalid trading session name: " + trade.tradeReport.sessionName
1270                    + ", current Open Session: " + openSessionName + " at " + getClass().getName()
1271                    + ".acceptTradeV2().";
1272            Log.alarm(this, message);
1273            throw ExceptionBuilder.notAcceptedException(message, NotAcceptedCodes.INVALID_STATE);
1274        }
1275 
1276        if (handlingInstruction != TradeReportHandlingInstructions.NO_TRADEREPORT_NO_TICKER
1277                && handlingInstruction != TradeReportHandlingInstructions.NO_TICKER
1278                && handlingInstruction != TradeReportHandlingInstructions.REGULAR
1279                && handlingInstruction != TradeReportHandlingInstructions.NO_TRADEREPORT)
1280        {
1281            String message = "DataValidationException thrown. Invalid Handling Instruction code in acceptTrade Code value passed="
1282                    + handlingInstruction;
1283            Log.information(message);
1284            throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException(message,
1285                    DataValidationCodes.INVALID_TRADE_REPORT_HANDLING_INSTRUCTION);
1286        }
1287 
1288        TradingProduct product;
1289        try
1290        {
1291            product = getTradingProductHome().findByKey(trade.tradeReport.productKey);
1292        }
1293        catch (NotFoundException e)
1294        {
1295            // this was already validated in isValidTrade
1296            String message = "Unable to access trading prodcut for product key "
1297                    + trade.tradeReport.productKey;
1298            Log.exception(this, message, e);
1299            throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException(message,
1300                    DataValidationCodes.INVALID_PRODUCT);
1301        }
1302 
1303        if (product == null)
1304        {
1305            String message = "Unable to access trading prodcut for product key "
1306                    + trade.tradeReport.productKey;
1307            Log.alarm(this, message);
1308            throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException(message,
1309                    DataValidationCodes.INVALID_PRODUCT);
1310        }
1311 
1312        if (isParTrade == false)
1313        {
1314            // validation product state condition
1315            if (!product.inTradingState())
1316            {
1317                // TODO does this rule apply to BLOCK_TRADE only or all types of manual trades?
1318                if ((TradeTypes.BLOCK_TRADE == trade.tradeReport.tradeType)
1319                        && (ProductStates.CLOSED == product.getCurrentStateCode())
1320                        && (isBlockTradeAllowedForClosedProduct(trade.tradeReport.sessionName)))
1321                {
1322                    if (Log.isDebugOn())
1323                    {
1324                        Log.debug("TradeServiceImpl: Block Trade for "
1325                                + trade.tradeReport.sessionName
1326                                + " allowed even though the Product state is Closed.");
1327                    }
1328                }
1329                else if ((TradeTypes.GWAP_TRADE == trade.tradeReport.tradeType)
1330                        && (ProductStates.CLOSED == product.getCurrentStateCode()))
1331                {
1332                    if (Log.isDebugOn())
1333                    {
1334                        Log.debug("TradeServiceImpl: GWAP Trade for "
1335                                + trade.tradeReport.sessionName
1336                                + " allowed even though the Product state is Closed.");
1337                    }    
1338                }
1339                else if ((TradeTypes.EXCHANGE_FOR_PHYSICAL == trade.tradeReport.tradeType)
1340                        && (ProductStates.CLOSED == product.getCurrentStateCode())
1341                        && (isBlockTradeAllowedForClosedProduct(trade.tradeReport.sessionName)))
1342                {
1343                    if (Log.isDebugOn())
1344                    {
1345                        Log.debug("TradeServiceImpl: EXCHANGE_FOR_PHYSICAL Trade for "
1346                                + trade.tradeReport.sessionName
1347                                + " allowed even though the Product state is Closed.");
1348                    }
1349                }
1350                else
1351                {
1352                    String message = "Unable to trade for product key "
1353                        + trade.tradeReport.productKey + ", when the product state is :("
1354                        + product.getCurrentStateCode() + ")";
1355                    Log.alarm(this, message);
1356                    throw ExceptionBuilder.notAcceptedException(message, 0);
1357                }
1358            }
1359        }
1360 
1361        // validate the trade
1362        if (!isParTrade)
1363        {
1364            isValidTrade(trade, product.getProductKeys().productType);
1365        }
1366        return product;
1367}

1369        /**
1370     * internal method to create trade report solely based on the struct passed in
1371     * 
1372     * @param trade
1373     * @param handlingInstruction
1374     * @param billings
1375     * @return
1376     * @throws SystemException
1377     * @throws CommunicationException
1378     * @throws AuthorizationException

1384            String remoteSessionName, short handlingInstruction, AtomicTradeBillingStruct[] billings)

1386            DataValidationException, NotAcceptedException, TransactionFailedException

1393        {

1413                    + e2.toString(), e2);
1414            throw e2;
1415        }

1417        return tradeReport.toStructV2(true); // true - include only Active trades
1418    }

1607private TradeReport validateTradeBustParameters(String tradingSessionName, CboeIdStruct tradeId)
1608throws SystemException, DataValidationException, NotAcceptedException
1609{
1610    String openSessionName = TradingSessionNameHelper.getOpenConfiguredSessionName();
1611    if (tradingSessionName == null || openSessionName == null
1612            || !openSessionName.equals(tradingSessionName))
1613    {
1614        String message = "Invalid trading session name: " + tradingSessionName
1615        + "Open Session: " + openSessionName + " at TradeService.acceptTradeBust().";
1616        Log.alarm(this, message);
1617        throw ExceptionBuilder.notAcceptedException(message, NotAcceptedCodes.INVALID_STATE);
1618    }
1619 
1620    //  verify that trade id is valid and that trade can be busted
1621    TradeReport tradeReport;
1622    try
1623    {
1624        tradeReport = getTradeReport(CboeId.longValue(tradeId));
1625        ((TradeReportImpl) tradeReport).turnOffPersistentBObjectInterceptor(true);
1626    }
1627    catch (NotFoundException nfe)
1628    {
1629        throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException(
1630                "Unable to find trade report for tradeId - " + tradeId, 0);
1631    }
1632    return tradeReport;        
1633}

1635    
1636    private TradeReport validateTradeBustParameters(MultipleTradeBustStruct tradeBustRequest) 
1637        throws SystemException, DataValidationException, NotAcceptedException
1638    {
1639        String tradingSessionName = tradeBustRequest.tradingSessionName;
1640        String openSessionName = TradingSessionNameHelper.getOpenConfiguredSessionName();
1641        if (tradingSessionName == null || openSessionName == null
1642                || !openSessionName.equals(tradingSessionName))
1643        {
1644            String message = "Invalid trading session name: " + tradingSessionName
1645            + "Open Session: " + openSessionName + " at TradeService.acceptTradeBust().";
1646            Log.alarm(this, message);
1647            throw ExceptionBuilder.notAcceptedException(message, NotAcceptedCodes.INVALID_STATE);
1648        }
1649 
1650        //  verify that trade id is valid and that trade can be busted
1651        TradeReport tradeReport;
1652        try
1653        {
1654            tradeReport = getTradeReport(CboeId.longValue(tradeBustRequest.tradeId));
1655            ((TradeReportImpl) tradeReport).turnOffPersistentBObjectInterceptor(true);
1656        }
1657        catch (NotFoundException nfe)
1658        {
1659            throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException(
1660                    "Unable to find trade report for tradeId - " + tradeBustRequest.tradeId, 0);
1661        }
1662        
1663        // Trade bust request for cross-product strategy trade at package level
1664        // can not be busted partially.
1665        int totalTradeBustQty = 0;
1666        for (BustTradeStruct atomicTradeBust : tradeBustRequest.tradeBustDetail)
1667        {
1668            totalTradeBustQty += atomicTradeBust.bustedQuantity;
1669        }
1670        if ((tradeReport.getTradeType() == TradeTypes.CROSS_PRODUCT_CROSS_TRADE) ||
1671            (tradeReport.getTradeType() == TradeTypes.CROSS_PRODUCT_LEG_TRADE) ||
1672            (tradeReport.getTradeType() == TradeTypes.CROSS_PRODUCT_AIM_CROSS_TRADE))            
1673        {                        
1674            if ((tradeReport.isParentReport()) && (tradeReport.getQuantity()!= totalTradeBustQty)) 
1675            {
1676                throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException("Cannot partially bust cross-product strategy trade at package level.", DataValidationCodes.INVALID_UPDATE_ATTEMPT);
1677            } 
1678        }
1679        if (tradeReport.getTradeType() == TradeTypes.HANDHELD_TRADE)
1680        {
1681            throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException("Cannot bust floor or carded trade.", DataValidationCodes.INVALID_UPDATE_ATTEMPT);
1682        }
1683        return tradeReport;
1684    }

1686    private List<TradeBustResponseStruct> bustRemoteTrades(TradeReport tradeReport,
1687            BustTradeStruct[] tradesToBust, String requestingUserId, String transactionId, DateTimeStruct timeStamp, 
1688            KeyValueStruct[] auditLogProperties) throws SystemException,
1689            CommunicationException, AuthorizationException, DataValidationException,
1690            NotAcceptedException, TransactionFailedException
1691    {
1692        ArrayList<BustManager> bustManagerList = new ArrayList<BustManager>();  
1693        TradingProduct product = findTradingProduct(tradeReport.getProduct());
1694        String tradingSessionName = product.getTradingClass().getSessionName();
1695        TradeValidationStrategy tradeValidationStrategy = getTradeValidationStrategy(tradingSessionName, product.getProductKeys().productType);
1696 
1697        BustManager bustManager = new CrossProductLegReportBust(tradeReport, tradesToBust, requestingUserId, 
1698                transactionId, timeStamp,  auditLogProperties);
1699        if (bustManager.isElgibleForClassLock())
1700        {
1701            processTradeBustWithLock(product, bustManager);
1702        }
1703        else
1704        {
1705            processTradeBustWithoutLock(bustManager);
1706        }
1707        bustManagerList.add(bustManager);        
1708        return collectTradeBustResults(bustManagerList);
1709    }
1710    
1711    private IntHashMap<List<TradeReport>> groupTradeReportsByProductKey(Vector reports)
1712    {
1713        IntHashMap<List<TradeReport>> reportsByProductKey = new IntHashMap<List<TradeReport>>();
1714        for (int index = 0; index < reports.size(); index++)  {
1715            int productKey = ((TradeReport) reports.get(index)).getProduct();
1716            List<TradeReport> reportListForProduct = reportsByProductKey.get(productKey);
1717            if (reportListForProduct == null) {
1718                reportListForProduct = new ArrayList<TradeReport>();
1719                reportsByProductKey.put(productKey, reportListForProduct);
1720            }
1721            reportListForProduct.add((TradeReport) reports.get(index));
1722        }
1723        return reportsByProductKey;        
1724    }
1725    private Map<Long, BustTradeStruct> allocateChildBustQuantityToAtomicTrades(List<TradeReport> childReports, 
1726            TradeReport strategyReport, int bustQuantity) 
1727    {
1728        Map<Long, BustTradeStruct> atomicTradeBustAllocation = new HashMap<Long, BustTradeStruct>();
1729        int bustQuantityCounter = 0;
1730        int bustQuantityAdded = 0;
1731        int bustQuantityRequired = bustQuantity * calculateLegRatio(strategyReport.getProduct(), childReports.get(0).getProduct());
1732        int iterationCount = bustQuantityRequired;
1733        
1734        while (bustQuantityCounter < bustQuantityRequired)
1735        {
1736            bustQuantityAdded = 0;
1737            for (TradeReport childReport : childReports)
1738            {
1739                TradeReportEntry[] atomicTrades = childReport.getEntries(true);
1740                for (TradeReportEntry anAtomicTrade : atomicTrades)
1741                {
1742                    if (anAtomicTrade.getQuantity() > 0)  
1743                    {
1744                        long lAtomicTradeId = anAtomicTrade.getAtomicTradeId();
1745                        BustTradeStruct bustRequest = atomicTradeBustAllocation.get(lAtomicTradeId);
1746                        if (bustRequest == null)
1747                        {
1748                            bustRequest = new BustTradeStruct();
1749                            bustRequest.atomicTradeId = CboeId.toStruct(lAtomicTradeId);
1750                            bustRequest.bustedQuantity = 1;
1751                            bustRequest.buyerReinstateRequested = false;  // Reinstate not allowed for strategies
1752                            bustRequest.sellerReinstateRequested = false; // Reinstate not allowed for strategies
1753                            atomicTradeBustAllocation.put(lAtomicTradeId, bustRequest);       
1754                            bustQuantityAdded++;
1755                        }
1756                        else
1757                        {
1758                            if (bustRequest.bustedQuantity < anAtomicTrade.getQuantity())
1759                            {
1760                                bustRequest.bustedQuantity += 1;
1761                                bustQuantityAdded++;
1762                            }
1763                        }
1764                    }
1765                } 
1766            }
1767            if (bustQuantityAdded == 0)
1768            {
1769                // We have gone through all trade reports and their atomic trades
1770                // and there is no more quantity remaining to bust in these trades.
1771                // Yet the strategy bust quantity is still not satisfied. Something is
1772                // wrong here. 
1773                //mismatchQtyWarning = "WARNING: Insufficient qty to bust in equity leg to match with requested bust qty, but busted whatever qty was present";
1774                break;
1775            }
1776            // Increment the strategy level quantity count
1777            bustQuantityCounter += bustQuantityAdded;
1778        }   
1779        return atomicTradeBustAllocation;
1780    }
1781 
1782    private Map<Long, List<BustTradeStruct>> organizeChildTradeBustRequests(List<TradeReport> childReports,
1783            Map<Long, BustTradeStruct> childTradeBustAllocationByAtomicTrade)
1784    {    
1785        Map<Long, List<BustTradeStruct>> bustRequestsForAllChildReports = new HashMap<Long, List<BustTradeStruct>>();
1786        for (TradeReport childReport : childReports)  
1787        {
1788            List<BustTradeStruct> bustRequestsForSingleChildReport = new ArrayList<BustTradeStruct>();
1789            TradeReportEntry[] atomicTrades = childReport.getEntries();
1790            for (TradeReportEntry anAtomicTrade : atomicTrades)
1791            {
1792                long lAtomicTradeId = anAtomicTrade.getAtomicTradeId();
1793                BustTradeStruct atomicTradeBust = childTradeBustAllocationByAtomicTrade.get(lAtomicTradeId);
1794                if (atomicTradeBust != null)
1795                {
1796                    bustRequestsForSingleChildReport.add(atomicTradeBust);
1797                }                 
1798            }
1799            bustRequestsForAllChildReports.put(childReport.getTradeId(), bustRequestsForSingleChildReport);
1800        }
1801        return bustRequestsForAllChildReports;
1802    }
1803 
1804    private List<TradeBustResponseStruct>  bustLocalTrades(String tradingSessionName, TradeReport tradeReport,
1805            BustTradeStruct[] tradesToBust,  String reasonDescription, boolean isMarketMakerRequestedBust, char marketMakerSide) 
1806            throws SystemException,
1807            CommunicationException, AuthorizationException, DataValidationException,
1808            NotAcceptedException, TransactionFailedException
1809    {
1810        ArrayList<BustManager> bustManagerList = new ArrayList<BustManager>();
1811        if (tradeReport.getQuantity() == 0) {
1812            throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException(
1813                    "Trade Report doesn't have enough quantity to bust for given TradeId " + tradeReport.getTradeId(), DataValidationCodes.INVALID_ID);                            
1814        }
1815        
1816        int productKey = tradeReport.getProduct();        
1817        if (tradeReport.isStrategyReport())
1818        {
1819            TradeReport parentTradeReport = tradeReport.getParentReport();
1820            // The trade report is for the strategy package level
1821            if (parentTradeReport == null )
1822            {      
1823                Vector childReports = tradeReport.getChildReports();
1824                if (childReports != null && childReports.size() > 0)
1825                {
1826                    // Determine the total bust quantity for the
1827                    // entire strategy to determine the bust quantity distribution
1828                    // across multiple trade reports and atomic trades at the leg level.
1829                    int strategyPkgBustQty = 0;
1830                    for (BustTradeStruct theBustStruct : tradesToBust)
1831                    {
1832                        strategyPkgBustQty += theBustStruct.bustedQuantity;
1833                    }                              
1834                    IntHashMap<List<TradeReport>> childReportGroupedByLeg = groupTradeReportsByProductKey(childReports);
1835                    Collection<List<TradeReport>> allGroupedChildReports = childReportGroupedByLeg.values();
1836                    for (List<TradeReport> childReportsForSingleLeg : allGroupedChildReports)
1837                    {
1838                        Map<Long, BustTradeStruct> bustQtyByAtomicTrade = allocateChildBustQuantityToAtomicTrades(childReportsForSingleLeg, 
1839                                tradeReport, strategyPkgBustQty);
1840                        Map<Long, List<BustTradeStruct>> bustRequestsByChildReport = organizeChildTradeBustRequests(childReportsForSingleLeg,
1841                                bustQtyByAtomicTrade);
1842                        for (TradeReport aChildReport : childReportsForSingleLeg)
1843                        {
1844                            String sessionName = aChildReport.getTradingProduct().getTradingClass().getSessionName();
1845                            long childReportId = aChildReport.getTradeId();
1846                            List<BustTradeStruct> bustRequestsForSingleReportForLeg = bustRequestsByChildReport.get(childReportId);
1847                            if (bustRequestsForSingleReportForLeg != null)  
1848                            {
1849                                for (BustTradeStruct atomicTradeBust : bustRequestsForSingleReportForLeg) 
1850                                {
1851                                    BustManager bustMgr = doExecute(aChildReport.getProduct(), aChildReport, 
1852                                            sessionName, atomicTradeBust, isMarketMakerRequestedBust, marketMakerSide);
1853                                    bustManagerList.add(bustMgr);
1854                                }
1855                            }
1856                        }
1857                    }
1858                }
1859                
1860                //Execute the strategy package trade bust.
1861                // Issue one BustReportManager per atomic trade. Each BustReportManagaer
1862                // is handed to an AcceptTradeBustCommand. The command is executed in an
1863                // independent transaction, thus we want to take advantage of ensuring that
1864                // if one atomic trade bust fails that not all atomic trade busts are not
1865                // rolled back. Otherwise we have to start inner transaction on a per
1866                // atomic trade basis. Let's avoid that. 
1867                for (BustTradeStruct aTradeBust : tradesToBust)
1868                {                    
1869                    BustManager bustMgr = doExecute(productKey, tradeReport, tradingSessionName, aTradeBust, isMarketMakerRequestedBust, marketMakerSide);
1870                    bustManagerList.add(bustMgr);
1871                }
1872            }
1873            else
1874            {
1875                int strategyProductKey = parentTradeReport.getProduct();
1876                int reqBustLegQty = 0;
1877                //Cache the original BustStructs
1878                for (BustTradeStruct theBustStruct : tradesToBust)
1879                {
1880                    reqBustLegQty += theBustStruct.bustedQuantity;
1881                }
1882                 
1883                try
1884                {
1885                    long theTradeId = parentTradeReport.getTradeId();
1886                    TradeReport parentReport = getTradeReport(theTradeId);
1887                    ((TradeReportImpl) parentReport).turnOffPersistentBObjectInterceptor(true);
1888                    TradeReportStruct parentReportStruct = parentReport.toStruct(true);
1889                    int packageBustQty = getAdjustBustQuantity(productKey, reqBustLegQty, parentReport, strategyProductKey);
1890                    //get bust struct for package level
1891                    BustTradeStruct[] bustStructs = getTradesToBustStructs(parentReport, parentReportStruct, packageBustQty, false);
1892                    // Execute the strategy leg trade bust first
1893                    for (BustTradeStruct aTradeBust : tradesToBust) 
1894                    {
1895                        BustManager bustMgr = doExecute(productKey, tradeReport,tradingSessionName, aTradeBust, isMarketMakerRequestedBust, marketMakerSide);
1896                        bustManagerList.add(bustMgr);
1897                    }
1898                    
1899                    if (bustStructs.length > 0) {
1900                        //Execute the strategy package trade bus
1901                        for (BustTradeStruct aTradeBust : bustStructs) 
1902                        {
1903                            BustManager theBustMgr = doExecute(parentReportStruct.productKey, parentReport, parentReportStruct.sessionName,aTradeBust, isMarketMakerRequestedBust, marketMakerSide);
1904                            bustManagerList.add(theBustMgr);
1905                        }
1906                    }
1907                }
1908                catch (Exception e)
1909                {
1910                    String msg = "Unable to bust the Trade Report for given tradeId = "  + tradeReport.getTradeId();
1911                    Log.exception(this,msg, e);
1912                    throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException(msg, DataValidationCodes.INVALID_ID);                            
1913                }
1914            }
1915        }
1916        else
1917        {
1918            for (BustTradeStruct aTradeBust : tradesToBust) 
1919            {
1920                BustManager bustMgr = doExecute(productKey, tradeReport,tradingSessionName, aTradeBust, isMarketMakerRequestedBust, marketMakerSide);
1921                bustManagerList.add(bustMgr);
1922            }
1923        }
1924        return collectTradeBustResults(bustManagerList);
1925    }
1926    
1927    private List<TradeBustResponseStruct> collectTradeBustResults(List<BustManager> bustManagers)
1928    {
1929        ArrayList<TradeBustResponseStruct> bustResults = new ArrayList<TradeBustResponseStruct>();
1930        for (BustManager aBustManager : bustManagers)
1931        {
1932            bustResults.addAll(aBustManager.getBustResults());
1933        }
1934        return bustResults;
1935    }
1936    
1937    private BustManager doExecute(int prodKey, TradeReport tradeReport, String tradingSessionName,
1938             BustTradeStruct tradeToBust,  boolean parTradeMMSideBust, char parTradeMMSide) throws DataValidationException, NotAcceptedException
1939    {
1940        // get the trading product
1941        TradingProduct product = findTradingProduct(prodKey);
1942 
1943        // find the appropriate BustTradeStrategy
1944        TradeValidationStrategy tradeValidationStrategy = getTradeValidationStrategy(tradingSessionName, product.getProductKeys().productType);
1945        BustManager bustMgr = executeCommand(product, tradeReport, tradeValidationStrategy, tradeToBust, parTradeMMSideBust, parTradeMMSide);
1946        return bustMgr;
1947    }
1948    
1949    private BustManager executeCommand(TradingProduct product, TradeReport tradeReport,
1950            TradeValidationStrategy tradeValidationStrategy, BustTradeStruct tradeToBust,  boolean parTradeMMSideBust, char parTradeMMSide) 
1951    throws DataValidationException, NotAcceptedException
1952    {
1953        BustManager bustManager = new BustReportManager(this, tradeReport, tradeToBust, parTradeMMSideBust, parTradeMMSide);
1954        bustManager.validateTheBust(tradeValidationStrategy);
1955 
1956        if (bustManager.isElgibleForClassLock())
1957        {
1958            processTradeBustWithLock(product, bustManager);
1959    }
1960        else
1961        {
1962            processTradeBustWithoutLock(bustManager);
1963        }
1964        return bustManager;
1965    }
1966    private void processTradeBustWithLock(TradingProduct product, BustManager bustManager)
1967    {
1968        boolean tradeReportBusted = false;
1969        boolean tradablesBusted = false;
1970        boolean transactionSuccess = false;
1971        boolean tradablesBustRequired = false;
1972 
1973        try 
1974        {
1975            Transaction.startTransaction();
1976            try
1977            {
1978                tradeReportBusted = bustManager.bustTradeReport(myIdService);
1979                tradablesBustRequired = bustManager.isBustTradablesRequired();
1980                if (tradeReportBusted && tradablesBustRequired)
1981                {                        
1982                    AcceptTradableBustCommand tradableBustCommand = new AcceptTradableBustCommand(bustManager);
1983                    product.acceptCommand(tradableBustCommand, false);
1984                    
1985                    // The AcceptTradableBustCommand executed via the CommandProcessor to 
1986                    // perform the bust of tradables inside class-level lock. The CommandProcessor
1987                    // for the trading class does not convey the Exceptions thrown during the 
1988                    // bust operations executed from within the AcceptTradableBustCommand.
1989                    // Therefore it is necessary to check the bust result from BustManager to 
1990                    // ensure that the tradable busting was successful. If not, then we
1991                    // need to roll-back the busting of the trade report that is performed
1992                    // outside of the CommandProcessor.
1993                    tradablesBusted = true;
1994                    List<TradeBustResponseStruct> allResponses = bustManager.getBustResults();
1995                    for (TradeBustResponseStruct bustResponse : allResponses) {
1996                        if (bustResponse.errorCode != ServerResponseCodes.SUCCESS)
1997                        {
1998                            tradablesBusted = false;
1999                            break;
2000                        }
2001                    }
2002                }                    
2003            }
2004            catch (Exception e)
2005            {
2006                // Do nothing. All exceptions are already handled
2007                // by the BustManager.bust() in that the exception error codes are recorded
2008                // in the TradeBustResponse struct, and the trade bust
2009                // is marked as UNSUCCESSFUL.
2010            }
2011            if (tradeReportBusted && (!tradablesBustRequired))  {
2012                transactionSuccess = Transaction.commit();
2013            }
2014            else {
2015                if (tradeReportBusted && tradablesBusted) {
2016                    transactionSuccess = Transaction.commit();
2017                }
2018            }
2019        }
2020        finally
2021        {
2022            if(!transactionSuccess)
2023            {
2024                Transaction.rollback();
2025            }
2026        }
2027    }
2028    
2029    private void processTradeBustWithoutLock(BustManager bustManager)
2030    {
2031        boolean tradeReportBusted = false;
2032        boolean tradablesBusted = false;
2033        boolean tradablesBustRequired = false;
2034        boolean transactionSuccess = false;
2035        try 
2036        {
2037            Transaction.startTransaction();
2038            try
2039            {
2040                tradeReportBusted = bustManager.bustTradeReport(myIdService);
2041                tradablesBustRequired = bustManager.isBustTradablesRequired();
2042                if (tradeReportBusted && tradablesBustRequired)
2043                {                        
2044                    tradablesBusted = bustManager.bustTradables();
2045                    bustManager.reinstateOrders();
2046                }                    
2047            }
2048            catch (Exception e)
2049            {
2050                // Do nothing. All exceptions are already handled
2051                // by the BustManager.bust() in that the exception error codes are recorded
2052                // in the TradeBustResponse struct, and the trade bust
2053                // is marked as UNSUCCESSFUL.
2054            }
2055            if (tradeReportBusted && (!tradablesBustRequired))  {
2056                transactionSuccess = Transaction.commit();
2057            }
2058            else {
2059                if (tradeReportBusted && tradablesBusted) {
2060                    transactionSuccess = Transaction.commit();
2061                }
2062            }
2063        }
2064        finally
2065        {
2066            if(!transactionSuccess)
2067            {
2068                Transaction.rollback();
2069            }
2070        }
2071    }
