8724 
8725    public TradeReportStructV2 acceptCrossProductLegTradeV2(String p_originatingSessionName,
8726            TradeReportStructV2 p_crossProductLegTrade, AtomicTradeBillingStruct[] p_billings,
8727            OrderStruct[] p_buyers, OrderStruct[] p_sellers) throws SystemException,
8728            CommunicationException, AuthorizationException, DataValidationException,
8729            NotAcceptedException, TransactionFailedException
8730    {
8731        TradeReportStructV2 tradeReportResponse = null;
8732        try
8733        {
8734            //Setting the Sellers Order to Thread Local to be used 
8735            //to mark Short Sale indicator while creating Trade Report 
8736            //database entry.
8737            TradeHelper.setSellersOrderIntoContext(p_sellers);
8738            tradeReportResponse = acceptCrossProductLegTrade(
8739                p_originatingSessionName, p_crossProductLegTrade, p_billings);
8740        }
8741        finally
8742        {
8743            TradeHelper.setSellersOrderIntoContext(null);
8744        }
8745 
8746        // SEDL 5922 (PITS 9034) - cross product drop copies in stock
8747        // When a cross product spread-to-spread trade prints in CBSX, the firms really
8748        // want a drop copy available in CBSX.  This is an interim solution to the problem:
8749        // we will locally publish a fill report w/out contra information for each of the
8750        // spread orders that are traded.  We publish these fills only after the CBSX trade
8751        // is accepted.
8752        //
8753        // The proposed long-term solution is to generate orders in CBSX that represent the
8754        // stock legs of the spreads, and have them execute as a tied cross in CBSX.
8755        //
8756        // - Sinclair, 3/18/08
8757        if (generateCrossProductDropCopies)
8758        {
8759            try
8760            {
8761                generateFillsForCrossProductLegTrade(tradeReportResponse, p_buyers, p_sellers);
8762            }
8763            catch (Exception ex)
8764            {
8765                Log.exception(this, "Failed to publish cross product leg fill report "
8766                        + p_crossProductLegTrade.tradeReport.tradeId.highCboeId + ":"
8767                        + p_crossProductLegTrade.tradeReport.tradeId.lowCboeId, ex);
8768            }
8769        }
8770 
8771        return tradeReportResponse;
8772    }
8773 
8774    private void generateFillsForCrossProductLegTrade(TradeReportStructV2 p_legTrade,
8775            OrderStruct[] p_buyers, OrderStruct[] p_sellers)
8776    {
8777        OrderStatusConsumer orderStatus = EventHomes.getOrderStatusConsumerHome().find();
8778 
8779        Map<Long, List<AtomicTradeStruct>> buyers = new HashMap<Long, List<AtomicTradeStruct>>();
8780        Map<Long, List<AtomicTradeStruct>> sellers = new HashMap<Long, List<AtomicTradeStruct>>();
8781 
8782        for (int i = 0; i < p_legTrade.tradeReport.parties.length; i++)
8783        {
8784            AtomicTradeStruct atomic = p_legTrade.tradeReport.parties[i];
8785            addToMap(buyers, atomic, CboeId.longValue(atomic.buyerOrderOrQuoteKey));
8786            addToMap(sellers, atomic, CboeId.longValue(atomic.sellerOrderOrQuoteKey));
8787        }
8788 
8789        Log.information(this, "Publish cross product leg fills for drop copies for "
8790                + p_buyers.length + " buyers and " + p_sellers.length + " sellers.");
8791        publishFills(orderStatus, p_legTrade, Sides.BUY, buyers, p_buyers);
8792        publishFills(orderStatus, p_legTrade, Sides.SELL, sellers, p_sellers);
8793    }
8794 
8795    private void publishFills(OrderStatusConsumer p_orderStatus, TradeReportStructV2 p_legTrade,
8796            char p_side, Map<Long, List<AtomicTradeStruct>> p_orderToTradeMap,
8797            OrderStruct[] p_orders)
8798    {
8799        for (long orderId : p_orderToTradeMap.keySet())
8800        {
8801            OrderStruct order = null;
8802            for (OrderStruct anOrder : p_orders)
8803            {
8804                long anOrderId = CboeId.longValue(new CboeIdStruct(anOrder.orderId.highCboeId,
8805                        anOrder.orderId.lowCboeId));
8806                if (anOrderId == orderId)
8807                {
8808                    order = anOrder;
8809                    break;
8810                }
8811            }
8812            if (order == null)
8813            {
8814                Log.alarm(this, "Cross product leg fill publish: failed to find " + p_side
8815                        + "-side order in order list " + orderId + " in atomic trades for trade "
8816                        + CboeId.toString(p_legTrade.tradeReport.tradeId));
8817                continue;
8818            }
8819 
8820            FilledReportStruct fill = new FilledReportStruct();
8821 
8822            List<AtomicTradeStruct> atomicTrades = p_orderToTradeMap.get(orderId);
8823            ContraPartyStruct[] contras = new ContraPartyStruct[atomicTrades.size()];
8824            int totalTraded = 0;
8825            for (int i = 0; i < atomicTrades.size(); i++)
8826            {
8827                AtomicTradeStruct atomicTrade = atomicTrades.get(i);
8828                contras[i] = new ContraPartyStruct();
8829                contras[i].user = (p_side == Sides.BUY)
8830                        ? atomicTrade.sellerOriginator
8831                        : atomicTrade.buyerOriginator;
8832                contras[i].quantity = atomicTrade.quantity;
8833                contras[i].firm = (p_side == Sides.BUY)
8834                        ? atomicTrade.sellerFirm
8835                        : atomicTrade.buyerFirm;
8836 
8837                totalTraded += atomicTrade.quantity;
8838            }
8839 
8840            order.userId = "";
8841 
8842            fill.contraParties = getTradeServiceHome().prepareContrasForPublic(contras);
8843 
8844            fill.account = order.account;
8845            fill.cmta = order.cmta;
8846            fill.executingBroker = order.userAcronym.acronym;
8847            fill.executingOrGiveUpFirm = order.orderId.executingOrGiveUpFirm;
8848            for (LegOrderDetailStruct legEntry : order.legOrderDetails)
8849            {
8850                if (legEntry.productKey == p_legTrade.tradeReport.productKey)
8851                {
8852                    Log.information(
8853                                    this,
8854                                    "Using leg clearing firm "
8855                                            + legEntry.clearingFirm.exchange
8856                                            + ":"
8857                                            + legEntry.clearingFirm.firmNumber
8858                        + " for cross product drop copy stock fill, replacing (in the fill report only) the original "
8859                        + "orderId.executingOrGiveUpFirm "
8860                                            + order.orderId.executingOrGiveUpFirm.exchange + ":"
8861                                            + order.orderId.executingOrGiveUpFirm.firmNumber);
8862                    fill.executingOrGiveUpFirm = legEntry.clearingFirm;
8863                    order.orderId.executingOrGiveUpFirm = legEntry.clearingFirm;
8864                }
8865            }
8866            fill.extensions = "";
8867            fill.fillReportType = ReportTypes.STRATEGY_LEG_REPORT;
8868            fill.leavesQuantity = order.leavesQuantity;
8869            fill.optionalData = order.optionalData;
8870            fill.originator = order.originator;
8871            fill.orsId = order.orsId;
8872            fill.positionEffect = order.positionEffect;
8873            fill.price = p_legTrade.tradeReport.price;
8874            fill.productKey = p_legTrade.tradeReport.productKey;
8875            fill.sessionName = TradingSessionNameHelper.getConfiguredSessionNames()[0];
8876            fill.side = p_side;
8877            fill.subaccount = order.subaccount;
8878            fill.timeSent = DateWrapper.convertToDateTime(System.currentTimeMillis());
8879            fill.tradedQuantity = totalTraded;
8880            fill.tradeId = p_legTrade.tradeReport.tradeId;
8881            fill.transactionSequenceNumber = 1;
8882            fill.userAssignedId = order.userAssignedId;
8883            fill.userAcronym = order.userAcronym;
8884            fill.userId = order.userId;
8885 
8886            // Since the CAS requires all fills to have a minimal transaction sequence number of 2,
8887            // We'll artificially bump up the order seq number to 2 for the drop copy.
8888            // Note that if we can have a scenario where the order will fill multiple times in a
8889            // single
8890            // transaction, the sequence number 2 may get repeated. We don't currently have this
8891            // scenario
8892            // (as of CD7.1)
8893            // - sinclair, 10/24/2008
8894            //
8895            if (order.transactionSequenceNumber < MIN_ORDER_SEQ_NUM_FOR_FILL)
8896            {
8897                order.transactionSequenceNumber = MIN_ORDER_SEQ_NUM_FOR_FILL;
8898            }
8899 
8900            Log.information(this,
8901                    "Publishing fill for drop copy support of cross product trades.  Fill details follow:\n"
8902                            + "  userId='"
8903                            + fill.userId
8904                            + "'\n"
8905                            + "  executingBroker='"
8906                            + fill.executingBroker
8907                            + "'\n"
8908                            + "  executingOrGiveUpFirm='"
8909                            + fill.executingOrGiveUpFirm.firmNumber
8910                            + ":"
8911                            + fill.executingOrGiveUpFirm.exchange
8912                            + "'\n"
8913                            + "  side="
8914                            + fill.side
8915                            + "\n"
8916                            + "  quantity="
8917                            + fill.tradedQuantity
8918                            + "\n"
8919                            + "  price="
8920                            + PriceFactory.create(fill.price)
8921                            + "\n"
8922                            + "  productKey="
8923                            + PriceFactory.create(fill.productKey)
8924                            + "\n"
8925                            + "  tradeId="
8926                            + CboeId.toString(fill.tradeId)
8927                            + "\n"
8928                            + "  numContraParties="
8929                            + contras.length
8930                            + "\n"
8931                            + "  order.transactionSequenceNumber="
8932                            + order.transactionSequenceNumber + "\n");
8933 
8934            p_orderStatus.acceptOrderFillReport(ConfigurationGroupHelper
8935                    .getPublishingGroupsForProcess(), StatusUpdateReasons.NEW, order,
8936                    new FilledReportStruct[] { fill }, "");
8937        }
8938    }

9043        public TradeBustResponseStruct[] acceptMultipleTradeBust(MultipleTradeBustStruct[] trades,
9044                        String requestingUserId, String transactionId, DateTimeStruct timeStamp, KeyValueStruct[] auditLogProperties)
9045                        throws SystemException, CommunicationException,
9046                        AuthorizationException, DataValidationException,
9047                        NotAcceptedException, TransactionFailedException 
9048        {
9049            TradeBustResponseStruct[] result = new TradeBustResponseStruct[0];
9050                Log.information(this, "acceptMultipleTradeBust invoked for user: " + requestingUserId);                
9051                synchronized(this)
9052                {
9053                    ArrayList<TradeBustResponseStruct> bustResults = new ArrayList<TradeBustResponseStruct>();
9054            BulkActionRequestHome bulkActionReqHome = getBulkActionRequestHome();
9055            BulkActionRequest requestDbId = null;
9056            try {
9057                requestDbId = FederatedServiceHelper.queryBulkActionRequest(bulkActionReqHome, requestingUserId, transactionId);
9058            }
9059            catch( Exception e) {
9060                Log.information("BulkActionRequestID not found : " + e.getMessage());
9061            }
9062                
9063            if (requestDbId == null) {
9064                requestDbId = FederatedServiceHelper.persistBulkActionRequest(bulkActionReqHome,
9065                        timeStamp, requestingUserId, BUST_OPERATION,
9066                        transactionId, RouteNameHelper.getRouteName(), auditLogProperties);
9067            }
9068            
9069            for (MultipleTradeBustStruct theTradeToBust: trades)
9070            {
9071                List<TradeBustResponseStruct> localResults;
9072                try
9073                {
9074                    TradeReport tradeReportToBust = validateTradeBustParameters(theTradeToBust);
9075                    localResults = bustLocalTrades(theTradeToBust.tradingSessionName, tradeReportToBust, 
9076                            theTradeToBust.tradeBustDetail, "", false, Sides.UNSPECIFIED);
9077                    bustResults.addAll(localResults);
9078                    persistBulkActionDtl(requestDbId, localResults, theTradeToBust.tradeBustDetail);
9079                    
9080                    // If this is a cross-product strategy trade report, submit the request
9081                    // to bust the remote leg trades.
9082                    if (isCrossProductStrategy(tradeReportToBust.getProduct()))
9083                    {                 
9084                        if ((tradeReportToBust.getTradeType() == TradeTypes.CROSS_PRODUCT_CROSS_TRADE) ||
9085                            (tradeReportToBust.getTradeType() == TradeTypes.CROSS_PRODUCT_LEG_TRADE) ||
9086                            (tradeReportToBust.getTradeType() == TradeTypes.CROSS_PRODUCT_AIM_CROSS_TRADE))            
9087                        {
9088                            List<TradeBustResponseStruct> remoteResults;
9089                            remoteResults = bustRemoteTrades(tradeReportToBust, theTradeToBust.tradeBustDetail,
9090                                requestingUserId, transactionId, timeStamp, auditLogProperties);
9091                            bustResults.addAll(remoteResults);
9092                        }
9093                    }
9094                }
9095                catch (NotAcceptedException nae)
9096                {
9097                    for (BustTradeStruct atomicTrade : theTradeToBust.tradeBustDetail)
9098                    {
9099                        TradeBustResponseStruct bustResponse = new TradeBustResponseStruct();
9100                        bustResponse.tradeId = atomicTrade.atomicTradeId;
9101                        bustResponse.serverId = RouteNameHelper.getRouteName();
9102                        bustResponse.errorCode = ServerResponseCodes.NOT_ACCEPTED_EXCEPTION;
9103                        bustResponse.description = "Unable to bust atomic trade report: " + nae.getMessage();
9104                        bustResults.add(bustResponse);
9105                    }                
9106                }
9107                catch (DataValidationException dve)
9108                {
9109                    for (BustTradeStruct atomicTrade : theTradeToBust.tradeBustDetail)
9110                    {
9111                        TradeBustResponseStruct bustResponse = new TradeBustResponseStruct();
9112                        bustResponse.tradeId = atomicTrade.atomicTradeId;
9113                        bustResponse.serverId = RouteNameHelper.getRouteName();
9114                        bustResponse.errorCode = ServerResponseCodes.DATA_VALIDATION_EXCEPTION;
9115                        bustResponse.description = "Unable to bust atomic trade report: " + dve.getMessage();
9116                        bustResults.add(bustResponse);
9117                    }                
9118                }
9119            }      
9120            result = new TradeBustResponseStruct[bustResults.size()];
9121            result = bustResults.toArray(result);
9122                }
9123        Log.information(this, "acceptMultipleTradeBust completed for user: " + requestingUserId);
9124        return result;
9125        }

9127    private boolean isCrossProductStrategy(int productKey)
9128    {
9129        boolean isCrossProductStrategy = false;
9130        ProductData prodData;
9131        try
9132        {
9133            prodData = getProductDataCacheHome().find().getProductData(productKey);
9134            if (prodData.isCrossProductStrategy())  
9135            {
9136                isCrossProductStrategy = true;
9137            }
9138        }
9139        catch (Exception e)
9140        {
9141            // This shouldn't really happen. So for now, let's just swallow the 
9142            // exception and move on.
9143            Log.alarm(this, "Encountered exception while attempting to confirm whether product is cross-product");
9144            Log.exception(this, "Encountered exception while attempting to confirm whether product is cross-product/", e);
9145        }
9146        return isCrossProductStrategy;
9147    }

9156            if (prodData.getProductType() == ProductTypes.EQUITY)  
9157            {

9161        catch (Exception e)

9164            // exception and move on.

9417        public static class TradeReportQueryByTimeTest extends BaseTest
9418        {

9429        public TradeReportQueryByTimeTest(String methodName)
9430        {
9431                super(methodName);                
9432        }
9433        
9434        /**
9435         * Prepare a set of test reports as follows. C1 and C2 are
9436         * real class keys configured for local trade server, while NC3 and NC4
9437         * are dummy class-keys not configured for local trade server. Product keys
9438         * P1 and P2 are irrelavant but we just want to keep some variety of 
9439         * product keys. The primary exchange walues E1 and E2 are also for the
9440         * purpose of having a variety of trade reports to ensure that this test of query
9441         * by time retrieves reports for variety of classkeys, productkeys, and
9442         * primary exchnages as long as the time criteria is met and the classkey
9443         * is configured for local trade server. For each combination of classkey
9444         * productkey and exchange, a copy of the report is added that is marked as
9445         * inactive. Note also that relative trade times are noted with base 
9446         * trade time marked as T. The increment in the trade times are in minutes.
9447         * The trade reports are created in order as follows. The tradeids are 
9448         * assigned sequentially.
9449         * 
9450         * TR1: C1, E1, P1, Active, T 
9451         * TR2: C1, E1, P1, Inactive, T+1
9452         * TR3: C1, E1, P2, Active, T+2 
9453         * TR4: C1, E1, P2, Inactive, T+3 
9454         * 
9455         * TR5: C2, E2, P1, Active, T+4
9456         * TR6: C2, E2, P1, Inactive, T+5
9457         * TR7: C2, E2, P2, Active, T+6
9458         * TR8: C2, E2, P2, Inactive, T+7
9459         * 
9460         * TR9: NC1, E1, P1, Active, T+8
9461         * TR10: NC1, E1, P2, Inctive, T+9
9462         * TR11: NC1, E1, P1, Active, T+10
9463         * TR12: NC1, E1, P2, Inactive, T+11
9464         * 
9465         * TR13: NC1, E2, P1, Active, T+12
9466         * TR14: NC1, E2, P2, Inctive, T+13
9467         * TR15: NC1, E2, P1, Active, T+14
9468         * TR16: NC1, E2, P2, Inactive, T+15
9469         * 
9470         * @throws Exception
9471         */ 
9472         
9473        private void prepareTestReportDetail() throws Exception
9474        {
9475                int classCount = 0;
9476                long tradeTime = startTradeTime;
9477                TradingClass[] allClasses = getConfiguredClasses();
9478                String exchList[] = {"NYSE", "NASD"};
9479                
9480                // First add test reports for trading classes configured
9481                // for local trade server.
9482                for (TradingClass tc : allClasses)
9483                {                        
9484                        if (tc.getProductType() != ProductTypes.STRATEGY)
9485                        {
9486                                expectedClassKeys[classCount] = tc.getProductClassKey();
9487                                for (int pk = 0; pk < 2; pk++)
9488                                {
9489                                        // Add one active and one inactive report for 
9490                                        // cobmination of (Class, Exchange)/Product.
9491                                        TestReportDetail aReport = new TestReportDetail();
9492                                        aReport.tradeReportDbId = tradeReportDbId++;
9493                                        aReport.tradeReportEntryDbId = tradeReportEntryDbId++;
9494                                        aReport.classKey = expectedClassKeys[classCount];
9495                                        aReport.primaryExchange = exchList[classCount];                                
9496                                         aReport.productKey = expectedProdKeys[pk];
9497                                         aReport.tradeTime = tradeTime;
9498                                         aReport.active = (byte) 1;
9499                                         testReportDetailList.add(aReport);
9500                                         tradeTime += TRADE_TIME_INTERVAL_MILLIS;
9501                                         
9502                                         TestReportDetail nextReport = aReport.getCopy();
9503                                         nextReport.tradeReportDbId = tradeReportDbId++; 
9504                                         nextReport.tradeReportEntryDbId = tradeReportEntryDbId++;
9505                                         nextReport.active = (byte) 0;
9506                                         nextReport.tradeTime = tradeTime;
9507                                         testReportDetailList.add(nextReport);
9508                                         tradeTime += TRADE_TIME_INTERVAL_MILLIS;
9509                                }
9510                                if (++classCount == 2)
9511                                {
9512                                        break;
9513                                }
9514                        }
9515                }
9516                // Now add the reports for a class not configured for the local trade server
9517                // This is done by adding a copy of the test reports created above 
9518                // except change the classkey to a value that is not
9519                // configured for local trade server.
9520                ArrayList<TestReportDetail> nonConfigCKReports = new ArrayList<TestReportDetail>(); 
9521                for (TestReportDetail aReport : testReportDetailList)
9522                {
9523                        TestReportDetail nextReport = aReport.getCopy();
9524                             nextReport.tradeReportDbId = tradeReportDbId++; 
9525                             nextReport.tradeReportEntryDbId = tradeReportEntryDbId++;
9526                        nextReport.classKey = nonConfigClassKey;
9527                        nonConfigCKReports.add(nextReport);
9528                        tradeTime += TRADE_TIME_INTERVAL_MILLIS;
9529                }
9530                testReportDetailList.addAll(nonConfigCKReports);
9531                endTradeTime = tradeTime;
9532        }

9558        /**
9559         * This test is for the trader report query by time. The query criteria is
9560         * set to retrieve ONLY ACTIVE trade reports between time startTradeTime+1 and 
9561         * endTradeTime-1. From the above list of TRx (x = 1..16), only TR5 and TR9
9562         * are expected.
9563         */ 
9564         
9565        public void testGetAllActiveTradeReportsByTime() throws Exception
9566        {
9567                int expectedReportCount = 3;  
9568                long[] expectedTradeIds = {1003, 1005, 1007};
9569                DateTimeStruct beginTime = DateWrapper.convertToDateTime(startTradeTime + TRADE_BY_TIME_QUERY_MILLIS);
9570                DateTimeStruct endTime = DateWrapper.convertToDateTime(endTradeTime - TRADE_BY_TIME_QUERY_MILLIS);
9571                RelatedTradeReportSummaryStruct[] reports = null;
9572                try 
9573                {
9574                        reports = getTradeMaintenanceService().getTradeReportsByTime(beginTime, endTime, "W_MAIN", true);
9575                }
9576                catch (NotFoundException nfe)
9577                {
9578                        fail("Zero reports were found.");
9579                }
9580                catch (Exception e)
9581                {
9582                        fail("Unexpcted error while querying report. Caught exception: " 
9583                                        + e.getClass().getName() + ". Exception message: " + e.getMessage());
9584                }
9585                // We should have all trade reports except for the one at the begining and one at the end.
9586                assertNotNull("The query returned NULL.", reports);
9587                assertEquals("Actual report count " + reports.length + 
9588                                " does not match expected count " + expectedReportCount, 
9589                                reports.length, expectedReportCount);
9590                for (RelatedTradeReportSummaryStruct rtrss : reports)
9591                {
9592                          TradeReportSummaryStruct[] relatedReports = rtrss.relatedTradeReports;
9593                        // This test case only for simple trades, so there should only be one report
9594                        assertEquals("Expected a single related report. ", 1, relatedReports.length);
9595                        assertEquals("Expected parent report index to be 0", 0, rtrss.parentReportIndex);
9596                        long tradeTime = DateWrapper.convertToMillis(rtrss.relatedTradeReports[0].timeTraded);
9597                        assertTrue("Report from outside query time interval", (tradeTime > startTradeTime) && (tradeTime < endTradeTime));
9598                        long tradeId = CboeId.longValue(rtrss.relatedTradeReports[0].tradeId);
9599                        boolean unexpectedReportFound = false;
9600                        for (long expectTradeId : expectedTradeIds)  
9601                        {
9602                                if (tradeId != expectTradeId) {
9603                                        unexpectedReportFound = true;
9604                                        break;
9605                                }
9606                        }
9607                        assertTrue("Unexpected report with tradeid = " + tradeId + " received.", unexpectedReportFound);                         
9608                }
9609        }
9610        }
9611         
9612    private int getAdjustedMinTradedQty(int theLegProdKey, int reqBustQty, TradeReport tradeReport, int strategyProductKey)
9613    {
9614        int minPkgTradedQty = 0;
9615        Vector childReports = tradeReport.getChildReports();
9616        Map<Integer, Integer> tradedQtys = new HashMap<Integer, Integer>();
9617        if (childReports != null && childReports.size() > 0)
9618        {
9619            TradeReport[] tradeReports = new TradeReport[childReports.size()];
9620            childReports.toArray(tradeReports);
9621            for (TradeReport theTrade : tradeReports)
9622            {
9623                Integer theQty = tradedQtys.get(theTrade.getProduct());
9624                if (theQty == null)
9625                {
9626                    tradedQtys.put(theTrade.getProduct(), theTrade.getQuantity());
9627                }
9628                else
9629                {
9630                    int theProduct = theTrade.getProduct();
9631                    tradedQtys.put(theProduct, tradedQtys.get(theProduct) + theTrade.getQuantity());
9632                }
9633            }
9634        }
9635 
9636        boolean isCrossProduct = isCrossProductStrategy(tradeReport.getProduct());
9637        TradingStrategyLeg[] legs = getStrategyLegs(theLegProdKey, strategyProductKey);
9638        ArrayList<Integer> minPkgTradedQtyForLegs = new ArrayList<Integer>();
9639        for(TradingStrategyLeg leg : legs)
9640        {
9641            int legRatio = leg.getRatioQuantity();
9642            int productKey = leg.getProductKey();
9643            if ( isCrossProduct && isEquityLeg(productKey)) {
9644                continue;
9645            }
9646            if (productKey == theLegProdKey) {                
9647                minPkgTradedQtyForLegs.add((tradedQtys.get(theLegProdKey) - reqBustQty) / legRatio);
9648            }
9649            else {
9650                minPkgTradedQtyForLegs.add(tradedQtys.get(productKey) / legRatio);
9651            }            
9652        }
9653         
9654        minPkgTradedQty = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
9655        for (Integer minPkgTradedQtyForLeg : minPkgTradedQtyForLegs)   {
9656            if (minPkgTradedQtyForLeg < minPkgTradedQty)  {
9657                minPkgTradedQty = minPkgTradedQtyForLeg;
9658            }
9659        }
9660        return minPkgTradedQty;
9661    }

9664    {
9665        TradingProduct strategyProduct = null;
9666        try
9667        {
9668            strategyProduct = getTradingProductHome().findByKey(strategyProductKey);

9670        catch(NotFoundException e)
9671        {
9672            Log.exception("TradeServiceImpl>>>Unable to find trading product",e);
9673        }
9674 
9675        return strategyProduct.getStrategyLegs();
9676    }

9701    
9702    private BustTradeStruct[] getTradesToBustStructs(TradeReport tradeReport, TradeReportStruct theReport, int reqBustQty, boolean isLegQty) 
9703    throws DataValidationException
9704    {
9705        if (reqBustQty == 0) {
9706            Log.debug(this, "No package bust report");
9707            return new BustTradeStruct[0];
9708        }
9709 
9710        Map<Long, Integer> remainingQtyOnAtomicTrades = new HashMap<Long, Integer>();
9711        boolean isExit = false;
9712        try {
9713            AtomicTradeStruct[] parties = theReport.parties;
9714            Vector<BustTradeStruct> bustStructs = new Vector<BustTradeStruct>();
9715            if(parties.length == 1){ // A single atomic trade - no need for looping
9716                AtomicTradeStruct anParty = parties[0];
9717                BustTradeStruct bustStruct = new BustTradeStruct();
9718                bustStruct.atomicTradeId = new CboeIdStruct();
9719                bustStruct.atomicTradeId.highCboeId = anParty.atomicTradeId.highCboeId;
9720                bustStruct.atomicTradeId.lowCboeId = anParty.atomicTradeId.lowCboeId;
9721                bustStruct.bustedQuantity = reqBustQty; 
9722                bustStruct.buyerReinstateRequested = false; 
9723                bustStruct.sellerReinstateRequested = false;
9724                isExit = true;
9725                reqBustQty = 0;
9726                bustStructs.add(bustStruct);
9727            }
9728            if(!isExit){  // more than one atomic trade, will need to distribute the busted quantity
9729                int i = 0;                        
9730                for (AtomicTradeStruct anParty : parties)
9731                {
9732                    long lAtomicTradeId = CboeId.longValue(anParty.atomicTradeId);
9733                    remainingQtyOnAtomicTrades.put(lAtomicTradeId, anParty.quantity);
9734                    BustTradeStruct bustStruct = new BustTradeStruct();
9735                    bustStruct.atomicTradeId = new CboeIdStruct();
9736                    bustStruct.atomicTradeId.highCboeId = anParty.atomicTradeId.highCboeId;
9737                    bustStruct.atomicTradeId.lowCboeId = anParty.atomicTradeId.lowCboeId;
9738                    bustStruct.bustedQuantity = 1; 
9739                    bustStruct.buyerReinstateRequested = false; 
9740                    bustStruct.sellerReinstateRequested = false;
9741                    i++;
9742                    reqBustQty--;
9743                    bustStructs.add(bustStruct);
9744                    if (reqBustQty == 0) {
9745                        isExit = true;
9746                        break;
9747                    }
9748                }
9749            }
9750            if(!isExit){
9751                int maxIterations = reqBustQty;
9752                for(int k = 0; k <  maxIterations; k++)
9753                {
9754                    for (BustTradeStruct theStruct : bustStructs)
9755                    {
9756                        long lAtomicTradeId = CboeId.longValue(theStruct.atomicTradeId);
9757                        Integer remainingQty = remainingQtyOnAtomicTrades.get(lAtomicTradeId);
9758                        if (theStruct.bustedQuantity < remainingQty)
9759                        {
9760                            theStruct.bustedQuantity += 1;
9761                            reqBustQty--;
9762                            if (reqBustQty <= 0) {
9763                                isExit = true;
9764                                break;
9765 
9766                            }
9767                        }
9768                    }
9769                    if(isExit){
9770                        break;
9771                    }
9772                }
9773            }
9774            BustTradeStruct[] bustStructArray = new BustTradeStruct[bustStructs.size()];
9775            bustStructs.toArray(bustStructArray);
9776            return bustStructArray;
9777        }
9778        catch (Exception e)
9779        {
9780            Log.exception(this, "Unable to find child Trade Report for given tradeId = "
9781                    + theReport.tradeId, e);
9782            throw ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException(
9783                    "Children Trade Report not found for given TradeId", DataValidationCodes.INVALID_ID);                            
9784        }
9785    }

9816    private void persistBulkActionDtl(BulkActionRequest requestDbId,List<TradeBustResponseStruct> tradeBustResponses,
9817            BustTradeStruct[] tradeBustDetail)
9818    {
9819        List<BulkActionDetailWrapper> actionDetailWrappters = new ArrayList<BulkActionDetailWrapper>();
9820        String resultCode = null;
9821        String parentResultCode = null;
9822        long theTradeId = 0;
9823        
9824        /**
9825         * incase of strategy bust, for child trade records in the bulk action table,
9826         * the result code is not being set as input bust action does not contain child 
9827         * atomic trade ids. ideally this should be addressed with Client input/interface change
9828         *  but to resolve the problem faster for ONE_MAIN 8.7 
9829         * release(conidering bust as low key operation as for as performance)
9830         * , the result code is dervied by walking through the list.
9831         */
9832        
9833        if(tradeBustResponses.size() > 1)
9834        {
9835                for (TradeBustResponseStruct theTradeBustResponse : tradeBustResponses)
9836                {
9837                        theTradeId = CboeId.longValue(theTradeBustResponse.tradeId);
9838                        for (BustTradeStruct theBustTrade : tradeBustDetail) 
9839                        {
9840                                if (theTradeId == CboeId.longValue(theBustTrade.atomicTradeId)) 
9841                                {
9842                                        parentResultCode = theBustTrade.buyerReinstateRequested ? "R" :
9843                                                (theBustTrade.sellerReinstateRequested ? "S" : "B");
9844                                         Log.information(this, "Inside persistBulkActionDtl, parentResultCode="+parentResultCode);
9845                                        break;
9846                                }
9847                        }
9848                        if(parentResultCode != null ) break;
9849                }
9850        }
9851        
9852        for (TradeBustResponseStruct theTradeBustResponse : tradeBustResponses)
9853        {
9854                resultCode = null;
9855                theTradeId = CboeId.longValue(theTradeBustResponse.tradeId);
9856                for (BustTradeStruct theBustTrade : tradeBustDetail) 
9857                {
9858                        if (theTradeId == CboeId.longValue(theBustTrade.atomicTradeId)) 
9859                        {
9860                                resultCode = theBustTrade.buyerReinstateRequested ? "R" :
9861                                        (theBustTrade.sellerReinstateRequested ? "S" : "B");
9862                        }
9863                }
9864                if(resultCode == null)
9865                {
9866                        Log.information(this, "Inside persistBulkActionDtl, ResultCode is Null for AtomicTradeId="+theTradeId+". So setting the parent result code.");
9867                        resultCode = parentResultCode;
9868                }
9869                actionDetailWrappters.add(new BulkActionDetailWrapper(requestDbId.getRequestDbId(),
9870                                theTradeId, resultCode));
9871        }
9872        
9873        FederatedServiceHelper.persistBulkActionDtl(actionDetailWrappters, getBulkActionDtlHome());
9874        
9875        }

9917    public int createNonQTrade(Tradable tradable, TradingProduct aProduct, OrderBook book,
9918            Price expectedEndingTradePrice, boolean isTradableInBook, boolean isTreatedLikeCustomer, boolean p_nonContingency)
9919            throws SpreadProcessingException, DataValidationException, SystemException
9920    {
9921        int allocatedQuantity = 0;
9922        boolean success = false;
9923        boolean tradeHappened = false;
9924 
9925        try
9926        {
9927            Side otherSide = tradable.getSide().getOtherSide();
9928            int quantityToAllocate = tradable.getQuantityAllowed();
9929            boolean nonQOnly = false;
9930 
9931            ArrayList oppositeParticipantLists = new ArrayList();
9932            ArrayList tradePrices = new ArrayList();
9933            ArrayList tradeQuantities = new ArrayList();
9934            // Mutually exclusive flags for nonQ and treatedLikeCustomer
9935            if (!isTreatedLikeCustomer)
9936            {
9937                nonQOnly = true;
9938            }
9939 
9940            int oppositeAllocatedQuantity = createParticipantLists(oppositeParticipantLists,
9941                    tradePrices, tradeQuantities, getPreferredFirmAcronym(tradable),
9942                    getPreferredFirmExchange(tradable), aProduct, book, otherSide,
9943                    expectedEndingTradePrice, quantityToAllocate, nonQOnly, false,
9944                    isTreatedLikeCustomer, tradable, p_nonContingency);
9945            if (oppositeAllocatedQuantity > 0)
9946            {
9947                ArrayList sameParticipantLists = new ArrayList();
9948                int sameSideAllocatedQuantity = createParticipantLists(sameParticipantLists,
9949                        tradePrices, tradeQuantities, tradable, null, oppositeAllocatedQuantity,
9950                        aProduct.getTradingClass());
9951                if (sameSideAllocatedQuantity != oppositeAllocatedQuantity)
9952                {
9953                    allocatedQuantity = 0;
9954                }
9955                else
9956                {
9957                    allocatedQuantity = sameSideAllocatedQuantity;
9958                    Side updatedSide = otherSide;
9959                    Tradable unBookedTradable = isTradableInBook
9960                            ? null
9961                            : tradable;
9962                    if (otherSide.isBuySide() || otherSide.isAsDefinedSide())
9963                    {
9964                        completeTrades(unBookedTradable, oppositeParticipantLists,
9965                                sameParticipantLists, tradePrices, tradeQuantities, book,
9966                                updatedSide);
9967                    }
9968                    else
9969                    {
9970                        completeTrades(unBookedTradable, sameParticipantLists,
9971                                oppositeParticipantLists, tradePrices, tradeQuantities, book,
9972                                updatedSide);
9973                    }
9974                    
9975                    tradeHappened = true;
9976                } // end else
9977            }
9978        }
9979        finally
9980        {
9981            if (tradeHappened)
9982            {
9983                OrderBookPriceDetailUndoLog.clear();
9984            }
9985            else
9986            {
9987                OrderBookPriceDetailUndoLog.undoChange();
9988            }
9989        }
9990        return  allocatedQuantity;
9991    }

9993    protected ParticipantList createParticipantListForFlexTrade(OrderBook currentOrderBook,
9994            Side tradableSide, Price tradePrice, int tradeQuantity, Tradable tradable,boolean isAuctionInitiatorSide)
9995    {

9999

10023    protected ArrayList getPriceDetailsForFlex(Side tradableSide, Price tradePrice, OrderBook orderBook, Tradable incomingTradable, boolean isAuctionInitiatorSide)
10024    {

10036        TradableList tradableList = takeoutFlexTradablesWithBetterOrEqualPrice(tradePrice, tradableSide, sideTradableList,orderBook.getTradingProduct().isStrategy(),isAuctionInitiatorSide);

10060    
10061    /**
10062     * return a collection of tradables from the tradable list whose prices are better than the price passed in
10063     *
10064     * Note: Assume that tradabels are sorted by price. Better price is at the front of the list.
10065     * @param isStrategy 
10066     */
10067    private TradableList takeoutFlexTradablesWithBetterOrEqualPrice(Price price, Side side, TradableList tradables, boolean isStrategy, boolean isAuctionInitiatorSide)
10068    {
10069        TradableList result = new TradableListImpl();
10070        boolean isTradablePrice = false;
10071        for (int i = 0, n = tradables.size(); i < n; i++) {
10072             
10073            if(isStrategy && isAuctionInitiatorSide)
10074            {
10075                isTradablePrice = side.areTwoPricesTradable(price, tradables.get(i).getPrice());
10076            }
10077            else
10078            {
10079                //isTradablePrice = side.isFirstBetter(price, tradables.get(i).getPrice());
10080                    isTradablePrice = side.isFirstBetterOrEqual(tradables.get(i).getPrice(), price);
10081            }
10082            if (!isTradablePrice ) {
10083                break;
10084            }
10085            else {
10086                result.add(tradables.get(i));
10087            }
10088        }
10089        if (result.size() > 0 ){
10090            tradables.removeRange(0, result.size());
10091        }
10092        return result;
10093    }

10224    private short getActivityTypeForStatus(TradeReport tradeReport)
10225    {
10226        short activityType = 0 ;
10227        String msg = "";
10228            
10229        switch(tradeReport.getTradeStatusCode())
10230        {
10231            case TradeStatus.PENDING_PRICE_ON_HOLD : 
10232                    activityType = ActivityTypes.TRADE_PRICE_ON_HOLD;
10233                    break;
10234            case TradeStatus.PENDING_LEG_PRICE_ON_HOLD : 
10235                    activityType = ActivityTypes.LEG_TRADE_PRICE_ON_HOLD;
10236                    break;
10237            case TradeStatus.REVIEW_PRICE :
10238                    activityType = ActivityTypes.TRADE_PRICE_APPROVED;
10239                    break;
10240            case TradeStatus.REVIEW_LEG_PRICE :
10241                    activityType = ActivityTypes.LEG_TRADE_PRICE_APPROVED;
10242                    break;
10243            default :                    
10244                    break;
10245        }
10246            
10247        
10248        return activityType;
10249    }

10251    private FilledReportStruct getFillReportForTradeEntry(TradeReport tradeReport, Order order, CboeIdStruct tradeId, short reportType, int productKey , Price newTradePrice, Price underlyingPrice, String initiatorUserId)
10252    {
10253        for(FilledReportStruct report :order.getFilledReports())
10254        {
10255            if(CboeId.isEqual(tradeId,report.tradeId))
10256            {
10257                report.fillReportType = reportType;
10258                report.productKey = productKey;
10259                report.extensions = getExtensionsForFillReport(tradeReport, report, reportType, newTradePrice, underlyingPrice, initiatorUserId);
10260                
10261                                if(newTradePrice.isValuedPrice())
10262                                {
10263                        report.price = newTradePrice.toStruct();
10264                                }
10265                return report;
10266            }
10267        }
10268        return null;
10269    }

10271    private String getExtensionsForFillReport(TradeReport report, FilledReportStruct fillReport, short reportType, Price newTradePrice, Price underlyingPrice, String initiatorUserId)
10272    {
10273            StringBuffer extensions = new StringBuffer(fillReport.extensions);
10274            
10275                extensions.append(ExtensionFields.CURRENT_TRADE_PRICE).append(DEFAULT_TAG_DELIMITER).append(newTradePrice.toString()).append(DEFAULT_FIELD_DELIMITER);
10276                extensions.append(ExtensionFields.ORIGINAL_TRADE_PRICE).append(DEFAULT_TAG_DELIMITER).append(report.getOriginalTradePrice().toString()).append(DEFAULT_FIELD_DELIMITER);
10277                extensions.append(ExtensionFields.ORIGINAL_PRODUCT_KEY).append(DEFAULT_TAG_DELIMITER).append(report.getOrigProd()).append(DEFAULT_FIELD_DELIMITER);
10278                extensions.append(ExtensionFields.PENDING_TRADE_RESPONSE_END_TIME).append(DEFAULT_TAG_DELIMITER).append(getRemainingReviewTimerForPendingTrades(report)).append(DEFAULT_FIELD_DELIMITER);
10279                extensions.append(com.cboe.idl.constants.ExtensionFields.UNDERLYING_SEC_PRICE).append(DEFAULT_TAG_DELIMITER).append(underlyingPrice.toString()).append(DEFAULT_FIELD_DELIMITER);
10280        extensions.append(ExtensionFields.INIT_BRKR_USER_ID).append(DEFAULT_TAG_DELIMITER).append(initiatorUserId).append(DEFAULT_FIELD_DELIMITER);
10281            
10282            return extensions.toString();
10283    }

10285    private long getRemainingReviewTimerForPendingTrades(TradeReport tradeReport)
10286    {
10287            long transactionTime = DateWrapper.convertToMillis(tradeReport.getTransactionTime());
10288            long pendingTradeReviewTimer = 0;
10289            try 
10290            {
10291                        pendingTradeReviewTimer = getTradingProduct(tradeReport.getOrigProd()).getTradingClass().getTradingPropertyPendingPriceReviewTimer();
10292                } 
10293            catch (DataValidationException e)
10294            {
10295                        Log.exception("Failed to find Trading product : "+tradeReport.getProduct(),e);
10296                }
10297            
10298            long reviewTimer = transactionTime + pendingTradeReviewTimer;
10299            return reviewTimer;
10300    }

10365        /**

10369        private void resolveTradePriceForPercentageStrategyTrades(TradeReport tradeReport, int productKey, Price underlyingPrice, TradingProduct product, String userId) throws SystemException, CommunicationException, AuthorizationException,
10370        DataValidationException, NotAcceptedException, TransactionFailedException, NotFoundException
10371        {

10373                Price newTradePrice = PriceFactory.create(underlyingPrice.toDouble() * (originalTradePrice.toDouble()/100));
10374                String sessionName = product.getTradingClass().getSessionName();
10375                
10376                //Set the new Trade Price, new Product key in package trade report.

10380                ProductMaintenanceService productMaintenanceService = InternalBusinessServicesHelper.getProductMaintenanceService();
10381                Vector<TradeReport> childReports= tradeReport.getChildReports();

10383                ProductKeysStruct[] legProducts = new ProductKeysStruct[tradingStrategyLegs.length];
10384                ProductStruct[] derivedFixedLegProduct = new ProductStruct[legProducts.length];

10392                        legProducts[i].productKey = childReports.get(i).getOrigProd();

10395                        {

10397                                strLegDefStruct[i] = AuctionRequestStructBuilder.buildStrategyLegDefinitionStruct();
10398                                strLegDefStruct[i].legProduct = legProduct;

10405                        }

10716    /**

10721    protected String getPendingTradeInitiator(TradableList tradables, String auctionInitiatorId) 
10722    {
10723        //Gets the user

10727        for(int i=0 ; i< tradables.size(); i++)
10728        {

10732            if( auctionInitiatorId != null && orderUserId.equals(auctionInitiatorId))
10733            {
10734                userId = orderUserId;
10735                break;
10736            }else
10737            {
10738                if(firstOrderRecTime == 0 || orderRecTime < firstOrderRecTime )
10739                {
10740                    userId = orderUserId;
10741                    firstOrderRecTime = orderRecTime ; 
10742                }

10746    }
10747   
10748    /**
10749     * Returns the initiator order side.
10750     * In the case where initiator or user has orders on both the sides , side will be decided on the basis of order time.
10751     * 
10752     * @author Cognizant Technology Solutions.
10753     */
10754    private Side  getUserSideForTrade(TradeReport tradeReport , String userId) throws DataValidationException, TransactionFailedException, NotFoundException
10755    {
10756        Side userSide = null;
10757        boolean  userIsBuyer = false;
10758        boolean userIsSeller = false;
10759        Order buyOrder =  null;
10760        Order sellOrder = null;
10761        TradeReportEntry[] entries = tradeReport.getEntries(true);
10762        for(TradeReportEntry entry : entries)
10763        {
10764            
10765            Order buyOrderInEntry = getOrderHome().findOrder(entry.getBuyOrderId());
10766            
10767            boolean  userIsBuyerForEntry = buyOrderInEntry != null && buyOrderInEntry.getUserId().equals(userId);
10768            if(userIsBuyerForEntry && buyOrder == null)
10769            {
10770                buyOrder = buyOrderInEntry;
10771                userIsBuyer = true;
10772            }
10773            else if(userIsBuyerForEntry && buyOrderInEntry.getSourceReceivedTime() < buyOrder.getSourceReceivedTime())
10774            {
10775                buyOrder = buyOrderInEntry;
10776            }
10777            
10778            Order sellOrderInEntry = getOrderHome().findOrder(entry.getSellOrderId());
10779            boolean  userIsSellerForEntry = sellOrderInEntry != null && sellOrderInEntry.getUserId().equals(userId);
10780            
10781            if(userIsSellerForEntry  && sellOrder == null)
10782            {
10783                sellOrder = sellOrderInEntry;
10784                userIsSeller = true;
10785            }
10786            else if(userIsSellerForEntry && sellOrderInEntry.getSourceReceivedTime() < sellOrder.getSourceReceivedTime())
10787            {
10788                 sellOrder = sellOrderInEntry;
10789            }
10790        }
10791        
10792        if(userIsBuyer && userIsSeller)
10793        {
10794            if(buyOrder.getSourceReceivedTime() < sellOrder.getSourceReceivedTime())
10795            {
10796                userSide  = buyOrder.getSide();
10797            }
10798            else
10799            {
10800                userSide  = sellOrder.getSide();               
10801            }   
10802        }
10803        else if(userIsBuyer)
10804        {
10805            userSide  = buyOrder.getSide();
10806        }
10807        else if(userIsSeller)
10808        {
10809            userSide  = sellOrder.getSide();
10810        }else
10811        {
10812             ExceptionBuilder.dataValidationException("Unable to get user side in given trade with trade id : " +tradeReport.getTradeId(), DataValidationCodes.INVALID_SIDE);
10813        }
10814        return userSide;
10815    }
